390static const Seconds pageScrollHysteresisDuration { 300_ms };

394#define WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(channel, fmt, ...) RELEASE_LOG(channel, "%p - [webPageID=%" PRIu64 "] WebPage::" fmt, this, m_identifier.toUInt64(), ##__VA_ARGS__)
395#define WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(channel, fmt, ...) RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(channel, "%p - [webPageID=%" PRIu64 "] WebPage::" fmt, this, m_identifier.toUInt64(), ##__VA_ARGS__)

397class SendStopResponsivenessTimer {
398public:
399 ~SendStopResponsivenessTimer()
400 {
401 WebProcess::singleton().parentProcessConnection()->send(Messages::WebProcessProxy::StopResponsivenessTimer(), 0);
402 }
403};
404
405class DeferredPageDestructor {
406public:
407 static void createDeferredPageDestructor(std::unique_ptr<Page> page, WebPage* webPage)
408 {
409 new DeferredPageDestructor(WTFMove(page), webPage);
410 }
411
412private:
413 DeferredPageDestructor(std::unique_ptr<Page> page, WebPage* webPage)
414 : m_page(WTFMove(page))
415 , m_webPage(webPage)
416 {
417 tryDestruction();
418 }
419
420 void tryDestruction()
421 {
422 if (m_page->insideNestedRunLoop()) {
423 m_page->whenUnnested([this] { tryDestruction(); });
424 return;
425 }
426
427 m_page = nullptr;
428 m_webPage = nullptr;
429 delete this;
430 }
431
432 std::unique_ptr<Page> m_page;
433 RefPtr<WebPage> m_webPage;
434};
435
436DEFINE_DEBUG_ONLY_GLOBAL(WTF::RefCountedLeakCounter, webPageCounter, ("WebPage"));
437
438Ref<WebPage> WebPage::create(PageIdentifier pageID, WebPageCreationParameters&& parameters)
439{
440 Ref<WebPage> page = adoptRef(*new WebPage(pageID, WTFMove(parameters)));
441
442 if (WebProcess::singleton().injectedBundle())
443 WebProcess::singleton().injectedBundle()->didCreatePage(page.ptr());
444
445 return page;
446}
447
448static Vector<UserContentURLPattern> parseAndAllowAccessToCORSDisablingPatterns(const Vector<String>& input)
449{
450 Vector<UserContentURLPattern> parsedPatterns;
451 parsedPatterns.reserveInitialCapacity(input.size());
452 for (const auto& pattern : input) {
453 UserContentURLPattern parsedPattern(pattern);
454 if (parsedPattern.isValid()) {
455 WebCore::SecurityPolicy::allowAccessTo(parsedPattern);
456 parsedPatterns.uncheckedAppend(WTFMove(parsedPattern));
457 }
458 }
459 parsedPatterns.shrinkToFit();
460 return parsedPatterns;
461}

463WebPage::WebPage(PageIdentifier pageID, WebPageCreationParameters&& parameters)
464 : m_identifier(pageID)
465 , m_mainFrame(WebFrame::create())
466 , m_viewSize(parameters.viewSize)
467 , m_drawingAreaType(parameters.drawingAreaType)
468 , m_alwaysShowsHorizontalScroller { parameters.alwaysShowsHorizontalScroller }
469 , m_alwaysShowsVerticalScroller { parameters.alwaysShowsVerticalScroller }
470 , m_shouldRenderCanvasInGPUProcess { parameters.shouldRenderCanvasInGPUProcess }
471 , m_shouldRenderDOMInGPUProcess { parameters.shouldRenderDOMInGPUProcess }
472 , m_shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess { parameters.shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess }
473#if ENABLE(WEBGL)
474 , m_shouldRenderWebGLInGPUProcess { parameters.shouldRenderWebGLInGPUProcess}
475#endif
476 , m_layerHostingMode(parameters.layerHostingMode)
477#if ENABLE(PLATFORM_DRIVEN_TEXT_CHECKING)
478 , m_textCheckingControllerProxy(makeUniqueRef<TextCheckingControllerProxy>(*this))
479#endif
480#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || PLATFORM(GTK)
481 , m_viewGestureGeometryCollector(makeUnique<ViewGestureGeometryCollector>(*this))
482#elif ENABLE(ACCESSIBILITY) && PLATFORM(GTK)
483 , m_accessibilityObject(nullptr)
484#endif
485#if PLATFORM(WIN)
486 , m_nativeWindowHandle(parameters.nativeWindowHandle)
487#endif
488 , m_setCanStartMediaTimer(RunLoop::main(), this, &WebPage::setCanStartMediaTimerFired)
489#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
490 , m_contextMenuClient(makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::PageContextMenuClient>())
491#endif
492 , m_editorClient { makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::EditorClient>() }
493 , m_formClient(makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::FormClient>())
494 , m_loaderClient(makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::PageLoaderClient>())
495 , m_resourceLoadClient(makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::ResourceLoadClient>())
496 , m_uiClient(makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::PageUIClient>())
497 , m_findController(makeUniqueRef<FindController>(this))
498 , m_inspectorTargetController(makeUnique<WebPageInspectorTargetController>(*this))
499 , m_userContentController(WebUserContentController::getOrCreate(parameters.userContentControllerParameters.identifier))
500#if ENABLE(GEOLOCATION)
501 , m_geolocationPermissionRequestManager(makeUniqueRef<GeolocationPermissionRequestManager>(*this))
502#endif
503#if ENABLE(MEDIA_STREAM)
504 , m_userMediaPermissionRequestManager { makeUniqueRef<UserMediaPermissionRequestManager>(*this) }
505#endif
506#if ENABLE(ENCRYPTED_MEDIA)
507 , m_mediaKeySystemPermissionRequestManager { makeUniqueRef<MediaKeySystemPermissionRequestManager>(*this) }
508#endif
509 , m_pageScrolledHysteresis([this](PAL::HysteresisState state) { if (state == PAL::HysteresisState::Stopped) pageStoppedScrolling(); }, pageScrollHysteresisDuration)
510 , m_canRunBeforeUnloadConfirmPanel(parameters.canRunBeforeUnloadConfirmPanel)
511 , m_canRunModal(parameters.canRunModal)
512#if ENABLE(META_VIEWPORT)
513 , m_forceAlwaysUserScalable(parameters.ignoresViewportScaleLimits)
514#endif
515#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
516 , m_screenSize(parameters.screenSize)
517 , m_availableScreenSize(parameters.availableScreenSize)
518 , m_overrideScreenSize(parameters.overrideScreenSize)
519 , m_deviceOrientation(parameters.deviceOrientation)
520 , m_keyboardIsAttached(parameters.keyboardIsAttached)
521 , m_canShowWhileLocked(parameters.canShowWhileLocked)
522#endif
523 , m_layerVolatilityTimer(*this, &WebPage::layerVolatilityTimerFired)
524 , m_activityState(parameters.activityState)
525 , m_userActivity("App nap disabled for page due to user activity")
526 , m_userInterfaceLayoutDirection(parameters.userInterfaceLayoutDirection)
527 , m_overrideContentSecurityPolicy { parameters.overrideContentSecurityPolicy }
528 , m_cpuLimit(parameters.cpuLimit)
529#if USE(WPE_RENDERER)
530 , m_hostFileDescriptor(WTFMove(parameters.hostFileDescriptor))
531#endif
532 , m_webPageProxyIdentifier(parameters.webPageProxyIdentifier)
533#if ENABLE(TEXT_AUTOSIZING)
534 , m_textAutoSizingAdjustmentTimer(*this, &WebPage::textAutoSizingAdjustmentTimerFired)
535#endif
536 , m_overriddenMediaType(parameters.overriddenMediaType)
537 , m_processDisplayName(parameters.processDisplayName)
538#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
539 , m_limitsNavigationsToAppBoundDomains(parameters.limitsNavigationsToAppBoundDomains)
540#endif
541 , m_lastNavigationWasAppBound(parameters.lastNavigationWasAppBound)
542#if ENABLE(APP_HIGHLIGHTS)
543 , m_appHighlightsVisible(parameters.appHighlightsVisible)
544#endif
545{
546 ASSERT(m_identifier);
547 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Loading, "constructor:");
548
549 m_pageGroup = WebProcess::singleton().webPageGroup(parameters.pageGroupData);
550
551 PageConfiguration pageConfiguration(
552 WebProcess::singleton().sessionID(),
553 makeUniqueRef<WebEditorClient>(this),
554 WebSocketProvider::create(parameters.webPageProxyIdentifier),
555 createLibWebRTCProvider(*this),
556 WebProcess::singleton().cacheStorageProvider(),
557 m_userContentController,
558 WebBackForwardListProxy::create(*this),
559 WebProcess::singleton().cookieJar(),
560 makeUniqueRef<WebProgressTrackerClient>(*this),
561 makeUniqueRef<WebFrameLoaderClient>(m_mainFrame.copyRef()),
562 makeUniqueRef<WebSpeechRecognitionProvider>(m_identifier),
563 makeUniqueRef<MediaRecorderProvider>(*this)
564 );
565 pageConfiguration.chromeClient = new WebChromeClient(*this);
566#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
567 pageConfiguration.contextMenuClient = new WebContextMenuClient(this);
568#endif
569#if ENABLE(DRAG_SUPPORT)
570 pageConfiguration.dragClient = makeUnique<WebDragClient>(this);
571#endif
572 pageConfiguration.inspectorClient = new WebInspectorClient(this);
573#if USE(AUTOCORRECTION_PANEL)
574 pageConfiguration.alternativeTextClient = makeUnique<WebAlternativeTextClient>(this);
575#endif
576
577 pageConfiguration.diagnosticLoggingClient = makeUnique<WebDiagnosticLoggingClient>(*this);
578 pageConfiguration.performanceLoggingClient = makeUnique<WebPerformanceLoggingClient>(*this);
579
580#if ENABLE(WEBGL)
581 pageConfiguration.webGLStateTracker = makeUnique<WebGLStateTracker>([this](bool isUsingHighPerformanceWebGL) {
582 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetIsUsingHighPerformanceWebGL(isUsingHighPerformanceWebGL));
583 });
584#endif
585
586#if ENABLE(SPEECH_SYNTHESIS)
587 pageConfiguration.speechSynthesisClient = makeUnique<WebSpeechSynthesisClient>(*this);
588#endif
589
590#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
591 pageConfiguration.validationMessageClient = makeUnique<WebValidationMessageClient>(*this);
592#endif
593
594 pageConfiguration.applicationCacheStorage = &WebProcess::singleton().applicationCacheStorage();
595 pageConfiguration.databaseProvider = WebDatabaseProvider::getOrCreate(m_pageGroup->pageGroupID());
596 pageConfiguration.pluginInfoProvider = &WebPluginInfoProvider::singleton();
597 pageConfiguration.storageNamespaceProvider = WebStorageNamespaceProvider::getOrCreate(*m_pageGroup);
598 pageConfiguration.visitedLinkStore = VisitedLinkTableController::getOrCreate(parameters.visitedLinkTableID);
599
600#if ENABLE(APPLE_PAY)
601 pageConfiguration.paymentCoordinatorClient = new WebPaymentCoordinator(*this);
602#endif
603
604#if ENABLE(WEB_AUTHN)
605 pageConfiguration.authenticatorCoordinatorClient = makeUnique<WebAuthenticatorCoordinator>(*this);
606#endif
607
608#if ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
609 pageConfiguration.applicationManifest = parameters.applicationManifest;
610#endif
611
612#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY) && ENABLE(DEVICE_ORIENTATION)
613 pageConfiguration.deviceOrientationUpdateProvider = WebDeviceOrientationUpdateProvider::create(*this);
614#endif
615
616 m_corsDisablingPatterns = WTFMove(parameters.corsDisablingPatterns);
617 if (!m_corsDisablingPatterns.isEmpty())
618 synchronizeCORSDisablingPatternsWithNetworkProcess();
619 pageConfiguration.corsDisablingPatterns = parseAndAllowAccessToCORSDisablingPatterns(m_corsDisablingPatterns);
620
621 pageConfiguration.userScriptsShouldWaitUntilNotification = parameters.userScriptsShouldWaitUntilNotification;
622 pageConfiguration.loadsSubresources = parameters.loadsSubresources;
623 pageConfiguration.allowedNetworkHosts = parameters.allowedNetworkHosts;
624 pageConfiguration.shouldRelaxThirdPartyCookieBlocking = parameters.shouldRelaxThirdPartyCookieBlocking;
625 pageConfiguration.httpsUpgradeEnabled = parameters.httpsUpgradeEnabled;
626
627 if (!parameters.crossOriginAccessControlCheckEnabled)
628 CrossOriginAccessControlCheckDisabler::singleton().setCrossOriginAccessControlCheckEnabled(false);
629
630#if ENABLE(ATTACHMENT_ELEMENT)
631 if (parameters.attachmentElementExtensionHandles)
632 SandboxExtension::consumePermanently(*parameters.attachmentElementExtensionHandles);
633#endif
634#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
635 // FIXME(207716): The following should be removed when the GPU process is complete.
636 static bool hasConsumedMediaExtensionHandles = false;
637 if (!hasConsumedMediaExtensionHandles && parameters.mediaExtensionHandles.size()) {
638 SandboxExtension::consumePermanently(parameters.mediaExtensionHandles);
639 SandboxExtension::consumePermanently(parameters.mediaIOKitExtensionHandles);
640 hasConsumedMediaExtensionHandles = true;
641 }
642 static bool hasConsumedGPUExtensionHandles = false;
643 if (!hasConsumedGPUExtensionHandles) {
644 SandboxExtension::consumePermanently(parameters.gpuIOKitExtensionHandles);
645 SandboxExtension::consumePermanently(parameters.gpuMachExtensionHandles);
646 hasConsumedGPUExtensionHandles = true;
647 }
648#endif
649
650#if HAVE(STATIC_FONT_REGISTRY)
651 if (parameters.fontMachExtensionHandle)
652 WebProcess::singleton().switchFromStaticFontRegistryToUserFontRegistry(WTFMove(*parameters.fontMachExtensionHandle));
653#endif
654
655 m_page = makeUnique<Page>(WTFMove(pageConfiguration));
656
657#if PLATFORM(IOS)
658 setAllowsDeprecatedSynchronousXMLHttpRequestDuringUnload(parameters.allowsDeprecatedSynchronousXMLHttpRequestDuringUnload);
659#endif
660
661 updatePreferences(parameters.store);
662
663#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY) || ENABLE(ROUTING_ARBITRATION)
664 DeprecatedGlobalSettings::setShouldManageAudioSessionCategory(true);
665#endif
666
667 m_backgroundColor = parameters.backgroundColor;
668
669 m_drawingArea = DrawingArea::create(*this, parameters);
670 m_drawingArea->setShouldScaleViewToFitDocument(parameters.shouldScaleViewToFitDocument);
671
672 if (parameters.isProcessSwap)
673 freezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::ProcessSwap);
674
675#if ENABLE(ASYNC_SCROLLING)
676 m_useAsyncScrolling = parameters.store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::threadedScrollingEnabledKey());
677 if (!m_drawingArea->supportsAsyncScrolling())
678 m_useAsyncScrolling = false;
679 m_page->settings().setScrollingCoordinatorEnabled(m_useAsyncScrolling);
680#endif
681
682 // Disable Back/Forward cache expiration in the WebContent process since management happens in the UIProcess
683 // in modern WebKit.
684 m_page->settings().setBackForwardCacheExpirationInterval(Seconds::infinity());
685
686 m_mainFrame->initWithCoreMainFrame(*this, m_page->mainFrame());
687
688 m_drawingArea->updatePreferences(parameters.store);
689
690 setBackgroundExtendsBeyondPage(parameters.backgroundExtendsBeyondPage);
691 setPageAndTextZoomFactors(parameters.pageZoomFactor, parameters.textZoomFactor);
692
693#if ENABLE(GEOLOCATION)
694 WebCore::provideGeolocationTo(m_page.get(), *new WebGeolocationClient(*this));
695#endif
696#if ENABLE(NOTIFICATIONS)
697 WebCore::provideNotification(m_page.get(), new WebNotificationClient(this));
698#endif
699#if ENABLE(MEDIA_STREAM)
700 WebCore::provideUserMediaTo(m_page.get(), new WebUserMediaClient(*this));
701#endif
702#if ENABLE(ENCRYPTED_MEDIA)
703 WebCore::provideMediaKeySystemTo(*m_page.get(), *new WebMediaKeySystemClient(*this));
704#endif
705
706 m_page->setControlledByAutomation(parameters.controlledByAutomation);
707 m_page->setHasResourceLoadClient(parameters.hasResourceLoadClient);
708
709 m_page->setCanStartMedia(false);
710 m_mayStartMediaWhenInWindow = parameters.mayStartMediaWhenInWindow;
711 if (parameters.mediaPlaybackIsSuspended)
712 m_page->suspendAllMediaPlayback();
713
714 m_page->setGroupName(m_pageGroup->identifier());
715 m_page->setDeviceScaleFactor(parameters.deviceScaleFactor);
716 m_page->setUserInterfaceLayoutDirection(m_userInterfaceLayoutDirection);
717#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
718 m_page->setTextAutosizingWidth(parameters.textAutosizingWidth);
719 setOverrideViewportArguments(parameters.overrideViewportArguments);
720#endif
721
722 platformInitialize();
723
724 setUseFixedLayout(parameters.useFixedLayout);
725
726 setUnderlayColor(parameters.underlayColor);
727
728 setPaginationMode(parameters.paginationMode);
729 setPaginationBehavesLikeColumns(parameters.paginationBehavesLikeColumns);
730 setPageLength(parameters.pageLength);
731 setGapBetweenPages(parameters.gapBetweenPages);
732 setPaginationLineGridEnabled(parameters.paginationLineGridEnabled);
733
734#if PLATFORM(GTK)
735 themeDidChange(WTFMove(parameters.themeName));
736#endif
737
738 effectiveAppearanceDidChange(parameters.useDarkAppearance, parameters.useElevatedUserInterfaceLevel);
739
740 if (parameters.isEditable)
741 setEditable(true);
742
743#if PLATFORM(MAC)
744 setUseSystemAppearance(parameters.useSystemAppearance);
745#endif
746
747 // If the page is created off-screen, its visibilityState should be prerender.
748 m_page->setActivityState(m_activityState);
749 if (!isVisible())
750 m_page->setIsPrerender();
751
752 updateIsInWindow(true);
753
754 setMinimumSizeForAutoLayout(parameters.minimumSizeForAutoLayout);
755 setSizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize(parameters.sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize);
756 setAutoSizingShouldExpandToViewHeight(parameters.autoSizingShouldExpandToViewHeight);
757 setViewportSizeForCSSViewportUnits(parameters.viewportSizeForCSSViewportUnits);
758
759 setScrollPinningBehavior(parameters.scrollPinningBehavior);
760 if (parameters.scrollbarOverlayStyle)
761 m_scrollbarOverlayStyle = static_cast<ScrollbarOverlayStyle>(parameters.scrollbarOverlayStyle.value());
762 else
763 m_scrollbarOverlayStyle = std::optional<ScrollbarOverlayStyle>();
764
765 setTopContentInset(parameters.topContentInset);
766
767 m_userAgent = parameters.userAgent;
768
769 // Do not overwrite existing items. Due to process swapping and back/forward cache support, there may be other
770 // (suspended) WebPages in this process for the same WebPageProxy in the UIProcess. Overwriting the HistoryItems
771 // would break back/forward cache for those other pages since the HistoryItems hold the CachedPage.
772 if (!parameters.itemStates.isEmpty())
773 restoreSessionInternal(parameters.itemStates, parameters.itemStatesWereRestoredByAPIRequest ? WasRestoredByAPIRequest::Yes : WasRestoredByAPIRequest::No, WebBackForwardListProxy::OverwriteExistingItem::No);
774
775 m_drawingArea->enablePainting();
776
777 setMediaVolume(parameters.mediaVolume);
778
779 setMuted(parameters.muted, [] { });
780
781 // We use the DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout milestone to determine when to unfreeze the layer tree.
782 m_page->addLayoutMilestones({ DidFirstLayout, DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout });
783
784 auto& webProcess = WebProcess::singleton();
785 webProcess.addMessageReceiver(Messages::WebPage::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier, *this);
786
787 // FIXME: This should be done in the object constructors, and the objects themselves should be message receivers.
788 webProcess.addMessageReceiver(Messages::WebInspector::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier, *this);
789 webProcess.addMessageReceiver(Messages::WebInspectorUI::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier, *this);
790 webProcess.addMessageReceiver(Messages::RemoteWebInspectorUI::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier, *this);
791#if ENABLE(FULLSCREEN_API)
792 webProcess.addMessageReceiver(Messages::WebFullScreenManager::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier, *this);
793#endif
794
795#ifndef NDEBUG
796 webPageCounter.increment();
797#endif
798
799#if ENABLE(SCROLLING_THREAD)
800 if (m_useAsyncScrolling)
801 webProcess.eventDispatcher().addScrollingTreeForPage(this);
802#endif
803
804 for (auto& mimeType : parameters.mimeTypesWithCustomContentProviders)
805 m_mimeTypesWithCustomContentProviders.add(mimeType);
806
807
808#if ENABLE(LEGACY_ENCRYPTED_MEDIA)
809 if (WebMediaKeyStorageManager* manager = webProcess.supplement<WebMediaKeyStorageManager>())
810 m_page->settings().setMediaKeysStorageDirectory(manager->mediaKeyStorageDirectory());
811#endif
812 if (parameters.viewScaleFactor != 1)
813 scaleView(parameters.viewScaleFactor);
814
815 m_page->addLayoutMilestones(parameters.observedLayoutMilestones);
816
817#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
818 setSmartInsertDeleteEnabled(parameters.smartInsertDeleteEnabled);
819 WebCore::setAdditionalSupportedImageTypes(parameters.additionalSupportedImageTypes);
820#endif
821
822#if HAVE(APP_ACCENT_COLORS)
823 setAccentColor(parameters.accentColor);
824#endif
825
826 m_needsFontAttributes = parameters.needsFontAttributes;
827
828#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
829 if (!parameters.iceCandidateFilteringEnabled)
830 m_page->disableICECandidateFiltering();
831#if USE(LIBWEBRTC)
832 if (parameters.enumeratingAllNetworkInterfacesEnabled)
833 m_page->libWebRTCProvider().enableEnumeratingAllNetworkInterfaces();
834#endif
835#if PLATFORM(COCOA) && ENABLE(MEDIA_STREAM)
836 if (auto* captureManager = WebProcess::singleton().supplement<UserMediaCaptureManager>())
837 captureManager->setupCaptureProcesses(parameters.shouldCaptureAudioInUIProcess, parameters.shouldCaptureAudioInGPUProcess, parameters.shouldCaptureVideoInUIProcess, parameters.shouldCaptureVideoInGPUProcess, parameters.shouldCaptureDisplayInUIProcess);
838#endif
839#endif
840
841 for (const auto& iterator : parameters.urlSchemeHandlers)
842 registerURLSchemeHandler(iterator.value, iterator.key);
843 for (auto& scheme : parameters.urlSchemesWithLegacyCustomProtocolHandlers)
844 LegacySchemeRegistry::registerURLSchemeAsHandledBySchemeHandler({ scheme });
845
846 m_userContentController->addContentWorlds(parameters.userContentControllerParameters.userContentWorlds);
847 m_userContentController->addUserScripts(WTFMove(parameters.userContentControllerParameters.userScripts), InjectUserScriptImmediately::No);
848 m_userContentController->addUserStyleSheets(parameters.userContentControllerParameters.userStyleSheets);
849 m_userContentController->addUserScriptMessageHandlers(parameters.userContentControllerParameters.messageHandlers);
850#if ENABLE(CONTENT_EXTENSIONS)
851 m_userContentController->addContentRuleLists(WTFMove(parameters.userContentControllerParameters.contentRuleLists));
852#endif
853
854#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
855 setViewportConfigurationViewLayoutSize(parameters.viewportConfigurationViewLayoutSize, parameters.viewportConfigurationLayoutSizeScaleFactor, parameters.viewportConfigurationMinimumEffectiveDeviceWidth);
856 setMaximumUnobscuredSize(parameters.maximumUnobscuredSize);
857#endif
858
859#if USE(AUDIO_SESSION)
860 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setShouldDeactivateAudioSession(true);
861#endif
862
863#if HAVE(VISIBILITY_PROPAGATION_VIEW)
864 m_contextForVisibilityPropagation = LayerHostingContext::createForExternalHostingProcess({
865 m_canShowWhileLocked
866 });
867 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Process, "WebPage: Created context with ID %u for visibility propagation from UIProcess", m_contextForVisibilityPropagation->contextID());
868 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidCreateContextInWebProcessForVisibilityPropagation(m_contextForVisibilityPropagation->contextID()));
869#endif // HAVE(VISIBILITY_PROPAGATION_VIEW)
870
871#if ENABLE(IPC_TESTING_API)
872 m_visitedLinkTableID = parameters.visitedLinkTableID;
873#endif
874
875#if ENABLE(VP9)
876 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setShouldEnableVP8Decoder(parameters.shouldEnableVP8Decoder);
877 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setShouldEnableVP9Decoder(parameters.shouldEnableVP9Decoder);
878 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setShouldEnableVP9SWDecoder(parameters.shouldEnableVP9SWDecoder);
879 if (m_shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess && WebProcess::singleton().existingGPUProcessConnection())
880 WebProcess::singleton().existingGPUProcessConnection()->enableVP9Decoders(parameters.shouldEnableVP8Decoder, parameters.shouldEnableVP9Decoder, parameters.shouldEnableVP9SWDecoder);
881#endif
882
883 m_page->setCanUseCredentialStorage(parameters.canUseCredentialStorage);
884
885 updateThrottleState();
886}

891#if HAVE(VISIBILITY_PROPAGATION_VIEW)

893#else
894 UNUSED_PARAM(gpuProcessConnection);
895#endif

899void WebPage::requestMediaPlaybackState(CompletionHandler<void(WebKit::MediaPlaybackState)>&& completionHandler)
900{
901 if (!m_page->mediaPlaybackExists())
902 return completionHandler(MediaPlaybackState::NoMediaPlayback);
903 if (m_page->mediaPlaybackIsPaused())
904 return completionHandler(MediaPlaybackState::MediaPlaybackPaused);
905 if (m_page->mediaPlaybackIsSuspended())
906 return completionHandler(MediaPlaybackState::MediaPlaybackSuspended);
907
908 completionHandler(MediaPlaybackState::MediaPlaybackPlaying);
909}

939
940void WebPage::reinitializeWebPage(WebPageCreationParameters&& parameters)
941{
942 ASSERT(m_drawingArea);
943
944 setSize(parameters.viewSize);
945
946 // If the UIProcess created a new DrawingArea, then we need to do the same.
947 if (m_drawingArea->identifier() != parameters.drawingAreaIdentifier) {
948 auto oldDrawingArea = std::exchange(m_drawingArea, nullptr);
949 oldDrawingArea->removeMessageReceiverIfNeeded();
950
951 m_drawingArea = DrawingArea::create(*this, parameters);
952 m_drawingArea->setShouldScaleViewToFitDocument(parameters.shouldScaleViewToFitDocument);
953 m_drawingArea->updatePreferences(parameters.store);
954 m_drawingArea->enablePainting();
955
956 m_drawingArea->adoptLayersFromDrawingArea(*oldDrawingArea);
957 m_drawingArea->adoptDisplayRefreshMonitorsFromDrawingArea(*oldDrawingArea);
958
959 unfreezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::PageSuspended);
960 }
961
962 setMinimumSizeForAutoLayout(parameters.minimumSizeForAutoLayout);
963 setSizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize(parameters.sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize);
964
965 if (m_activityState != parameters.activityState)
966 setActivityState(parameters.activityState, ActivityStateChangeAsynchronous, [] { });
967 if (m_layerHostingMode != parameters.layerHostingMode)
968 setLayerHostingMode(parameters.layerHostingMode);
969
970 platformReinitialize();
971}
972
973void WebPage::updateThrottleState()
974{
975 bool isThrottleable = this->isThrottleable();
976
977 // The UserActivity prevents App Nap. So if we want to allow App Nap of the page, stop the activity.
978 // If the page should not be app nap'd, start it.
979 if (isThrottleable)
980 m_userActivity.stop();
981 else
982 m_userActivity.start();
983
984#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
985 if (RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().serviceWorkerEnabled()) {
986 RunLoop::main().dispatch([isThrottleable] {
987 WebServiceWorkerProvider::singleton().updateThrottleState(isThrottleable);
988 });
989 }
990#endif
991}
992
993bool WebPage::isThrottleable() const
994{
995 bool isActive = m_activityState.containsAny({ ActivityState::IsLoading, ActivityState::IsAudible, ActivityState::IsCapturingMedia, ActivityState::WindowIsActive });
996 bool isVisuallyIdle = m_activityState.contains(ActivityState::IsVisuallyIdle);
997
998 return m_isAppNapEnabled && !isActive && isVisuallyIdle;
999}
1000
1001WebPage::~WebPage()
1002{
1003 ASSERT(!m_page);
1004 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Loading, "destructor:");
1005
1006 if (!m_corsDisablingPatterns.isEmpty()) {
1007 m_corsDisablingPatterns.clear();
1008 synchronizeCORSDisablingPatternsWithNetworkProcess();
1009 }
1010
1011 platformDetach();
1012
1013 m_sandboxExtensionTracker.invalidate();
1014
1015 for (auto* pluginView : m_pluginViews)
1016 pluginView->webPageDestroyed();
1017
1018#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1019 if (m_headerBanner)
1020 m_headerBanner->detachFromPage();
1021 if (m_footerBanner)
1022 m_footerBanner->detachFromPage();
1023#endif // !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1024
1025#ifndef NDEBUG
1026 webPageCounter.decrement();
1027#endif
1028
1029#if ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS) && HAVE(VISIBILITY_PROPAGATION_VIEW)
1030 if (auto* gpuProcessConnection = WebProcess::singleton().existingGPUProcessConnection())
1031 gpuProcessConnection->destroyVisibilityPropagationContextForPage(*this);
1032#endif // ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
1033
1034#if ENABLE(VIDEO_PRESENTATION_MODE)
1035 if (m_playbackSessionManager)
1036 m_playbackSessionManager->invalidate();
1037
1038 if (m_videoFullscreenManager)
1039 m_videoFullscreenManager->invalidate();
1040#endif
1041
1042 for (auto& completionHandler : std::exchange(m_markLayersAsVolatileCompletionHandlers, { }))
1043 completionHandler(false);
1044
1045#if ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
1046 for (auto& completionHandler : m_applicationManifestFetchCallbackMap.values()) {
1047 if (completionHandler)
1048 completionHandler(std::nullopt);
1049 }
1050#endif
1051}

1056}

1058uint64_t WebPage::messageSenderDestinationID() const

1061}

1141#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
1142
1143RefPtr<Plugin> WebPage::createPlugin(WebFrame* frame, HTMLPlugInElement* pluginElement, const Plugin::Parameters& parameters, String& newMIMEType)
1144{
1145 String frameURLString = frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader()->responseURL().string();
1146 String pageURLString = m_page->mainFrame().loader().documentLoader()->responseURL().string();
1147
1148 bool allowOnlyApplicationPlugins = !frame->coreFrame()->arePluginsEnabled();
1149
1150 uint64_t pluginProcessToken;
1151 uint32_t pluginLoadPolicy;
1152 String unavailabilityDescription;
1153 bool isUnsupported;
1154 if (!sendSync(Messages::WebPageProxy::FindPlugin(parameters.mimeType, parameters.url.string(), frameURLString, pageURLString, allowOnlyApplicationPlugins), Messages::WebPageProxy::FindPlugin::Reply(pluginProcessToken, newMIMEType, pluginLoadPolicy, unavailabilityDescription, isUnsupported)))
1155 return nullptr;
1156
1157 PluginModuleLoadPolicy loadPolicy = static_cast<PluginModuleLoadPolicy>(pluginLoadPolicy);
1158 bool isBlockedPlugin = (loadPolicy == PluginModuleBlockedForSecurity) || (loadPolicy == PluginModuleBlockedForCompatibility);
1159
1160 if (isUnsupported || isBlockedPlugin || !pluginProcessToken) {
1161#if ENABLE(PDFKIT_PLUGIN)
1162 if (shouldUsePDFPlugin(parameters.mimeType, parameters.url.path()))
1163 return PDFPlugin::create(*frame);
1164#endif
1165 }
1166
1167 if (isUnsupported) {
1168 pluginElement->setReplacement(RenderEmbeddedObject::UnsupportedPlugin, unavailabilityDescription);
1169 return nullptr;
1170 }
1171
1172 if (isBlockedPlugin) {
1173 bool isReplacementObscured = pluginElement->setReplacement(RenderEmbeddedObject::InsecurePluginVersion, unavailabilityDescription);
1174 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidBlockInsecurePluginVersion(parameters.mimeType, parameters.url.string(), frameURLString, pageURLString, isReplacementObscured));
1175 return nullptr;
1176 }
1177
1178 if (!pluginProcessToken)
1179 return nullptr;
1180
1181 return PluginProxy::create(pluginProcessToken);
1182}
1183#endif // ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)

1189}

1191WebCore::WebGLLoadPolicy WebPage::resolveWebGLPolicyForURL(WebFrame*, const URL&)
1192{

1194}
1195#endif
1196
1197EditorState WebPage::editorState(ShouldPerformLayout shouldPerformLayout) const
1198{
1199 // Ref the frame because this function may perform layout, which may cause frame destruction.
1200 Ref<Frame> frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
1201
1202 EditorState result;
1203
1204 if (PluginView* pluginView = focusedPluginViewForFrame(frame)) {
1205 if (!pluginView->getSelectionString().isNull()) {
1206 result.selectionIsNone = false;
1207 result.selectionIsRange = true;
1208 result.isInPlugin = true;
1209 return result;
1210 }
1211 }
1212
1213 const VisibleSelection& selection = frame->selection().selection();
1214 auto& editor = frame->editor();
1215
1216 result.transactionID = m_lastEditorStateTransactionID.increment();
1217 result.selectionIsNone = selection.isNone();
1218 result.selectionIsRange = selection.isRange();
1219 result.isContentEditable = selection.isContentEditable();
1220 result.isContentRichlyEditable = selection.isContentRichlyEditable();
1221 result.isInPasswordField = selection.isInPasswordField();
1222 result.hasComposition = editor.hasComposition();
1223 result.shouldIgnoreSelectionChanges = editor.ignoreSelectionChanges() || (editor.client() && !editor.client()->shouldRevealCurrentSelectionAfterInsertion());
1224
1225 Ref<Document> document = *frame->document();
1226 result.originIdentifierForPasteboard = document->originIdentifierForPasteboard();
1227
1228 if (result.selectionIsRange) {
1229 auto selectionRange = selection.range();
1230 result.selectionIsRangeInsideImageOverlay = selectionRange && HTMLElement::isInsideImageOverlay(*selectionRange);
1231 }
1232
1233 if (shouldPerformLayout == ShouldPerformLayout::Yes || platformNeedsLayoutForEditorState(frame))
1234 document->updateLayout(); // May cause document destruction
1235
1236 if (auto* frameView = document->view(); frameView && !frameView->needsLayout()) {
1237 result.isMissingPostLayoutData = false;
1238
1239 auto& postLayoutData = result.postLayoutData();
1240 postLayoutData.canCut = editor.canCut();
1241 postLayoutData.canCopy = editor.canCopy();
1242 postLayoutData.canPaste = editor.canPaste();
1243
1244 if (m_needsFontAttributes)
1245 postLayoutData.fontAttributes = editor.fontAttributesAtSelectionStart();
1246 }
1247
1248 getPlatformEditorState(frame, result);
1249
1250 m_lastEditorStateWasContentEditable = result.isContentEditable ? EditorStateIsContentEditable::Yes : EditorStateIsContentEditable::No;
1251
1252 return result;
1253}
1254
1255void WebPage::changeFontAttributes(WebCore::FontAttributeChanges&& changes)

1258 if (frame.selection().selection().isContentEditable())
1259 frame.editor().applyStyleToSelection(changes.createEditingStyle(), changes.editAction(), Editor::ColorFilterMode::InvertColor);
1260}

1262void WebPage::changeFont(WebCore::FontChanges&& changes)

1295void WebPage::updateEditorStateAfterLayoutIfEditabilityChanged()
1296{
1297 // FIXME: We should update EditorStateIsContentEditable to track whether the state is richly
1298 // editable or plainttext-only.
1299 if (m_lastEditorStateWasContentEditable == EditorStateIsContentEditable::Unset)
1300 return;
1301
1302 Frame& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
1303 EditorStateIsContentEditable editorStateIsContentEditable = frame.selection().selection().isContentEditable() ? EditorStateIsContentEditable::Yes : EditorStateIsContentEditable::No;
1304 if (m_lastEditorStateWasContentEditable != editorStateIsContentEditable)
1305 scheduleFullEditorStateUpdate();
1306}
1307
1308static OptionSet<RenderAsTextFlag> toRenderAsTextFlags(unsigned options)
1309{
1310 OptionSet<RenderAsTextFlag> flags;
1311
1312 if (options & RenderTreeShowAllLayers)
1313 flags.add(RenderAsTextFlag::ShowAllLayers);
1314 if (options & RenderTreeShowLayerNesting)
1315 flags.add(RenderAsTextFlag::ShowLayerNesting);
1316 if (options & RenderTreeShowCompositedLayers)
1317 flags.add(RenderAsTextFlag::ShowCompositedLayers);
1318 if (options & RenderTreeShowOverflow)
1319 flags.add(RenderAsTextFlag::ShowOverflow);
1320 if (options & RenderTreeShowSVGGeometry)
1321 flags.add(RenderAsTextFlag::ShowSVGGeometry);
1322 if (options & RenderTreeShowLayerFragments)
1323 flags.add(RenderAsTextFlag::ShowLayerFragments);
1324
1325 return flags;
1326}

1329{
1330 return externalRepresentation(m_mainFrame->coreFrame(), toRenderAsTextFlags(options));
1331}

1376
1377Ref<API::Array> WebPage::trackedRepaintRects()
1378{
1379 FrameView* view = mainFrameView();
1380 if (!view)
1381 return API::Array::create();
1382
1383 Vector<RefPtr<API::Object>> repaintRects;
1384 repaintRects.reserveInitialCapacity(view->trackedRepaintRects().size());
1385
1386 for (const auto& repaintRect : view->trackedRepaintRects())
1387 repaintRects.uncheckedAppend(API::Rect::create(toAPI(repaintRect)));
1388
1389 return API::Array::create(WTFMove(repaintRects));
1390}
1391
1392PluginView* WebPage::focusedPluginViewForFrame(Frame& frame)
1393{
1394 if (!is<PluginDocument>(frame.document()))
1395 return nullptr;
1396
1397 auto& pluginDocument = downcast<PluginDocument>(*frame.document());
1398 if (pluginDocument.focusedElement() != pluginDocument.pluginElement())
1399 return nullptr;
1400
1401 return pluginViewForFrame(&frame);
1402}
1403
1404PluginView* WebPage::pluginViewForFrame(Frame* frame)
1405{
1406 if (!frame || !is<PluginDocument>(frame->document()))
1407 return nullptr;
1408
1409 auto& document = downcast<PluginDocument>(*frame->document());
1410 return static_cast<PluginView*>(document.pluginWidget());
1411}

1413void WebPage::executeEditingCommand(const String& commandName, const String& argument)

1416
1417 auto& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
1418

1420 pluginView->handleEditingCommand(commandName, argument);
1421 return;
1422 }
1423
1424 frame.editor().command(commandName).execute(argument);
1425}

1434 // If the page is made editable and the selection is empty, set it to something.
1435 if (frame.selection().isNone())
1436 frame.selection().setSelectionFromNone();
1437 }

1486
1487void WebPage::close()
1488{
1489 if (m_isClosed)
1490 return;
1491
1492 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Loading, "close:");
1493
1494 WebProcess::singleton().ensureNetworkProcessConnection().connection().send(Messages::NetworkConnectionToWebProcess::ClearPageSpecificData(m_identifier), 0);
1495
1496 m_isClosed = true;
1497
1498 // If there is still no URL, then we never loaded anything in this page, so nothing to report.
1499 if (!mainWebFrame().url().isEmpty())
1500 reportUsedFeatures();
1501
1502 if (WebProcess::singleton().injectedBundle())
1503 WebProcess::singleton().injectedBundle()->willDestroyPage(this);
1504
1505 if (m_inspector) {
1506 m_inspector->disconnectFromPage();
1507 m_inspector = nullptr;
1508 }
1509
1510 m_page->inspectorController().disconnectAllFrontends();
1511
1512#if ENABLE(FULLSCREEN_API)
1513 m_fullScreenManager = nullptr;
1514#endif
1515
1516 if (m_activePopupMenu) {
1517 m_activePopupMenu->disconnectFromPage();
1518 m_activePopupMenu = nullptr;
1519 }
1520
1521 if (m_activeOpenPanelResultListener) {
1522 m_activeOpenPanelResultListener->disconnectFromPage();
1523 m_activeOpenPanelResultListener = nullptr;
1524 }
1525
1526#if ENABLE(INPUT_TYPE_COLOR)
1527 if (m_activeColorChooser) {
1528 m_activeColorChooser->disconnectFromPage();
1529 m_activeColorChooser = nullptr;
1530 }
1531#endif
1532
1533#if PLATFORM(GTK)
1534 if (m_printOperation) {
1535 m_printOperation->disconnectFromPage();
1536 m_printOperation = nullptr;
1537 }
1538#endif
1539
1540#if ENABLE(VIDEO) && USE(GSTREAMER)
1541 if (m_installMediaPluginsCallback) {
1542 m_installMediaPluginsCallback->invalidate();
1543 m_installMediaPluginsCallback = nullptr;
1544 }
1545#endif
1546
1547 m_sandboxExtensionTracker.invalidate();
1548
1549#if ENABLE(TEXT_AUTOSIZING)
1550 m_textAutoSizingAdjustmentTimer.stop();
1551#endif
1552
1553#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
1554 m_contextMenuClient = makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::PageContextMenuClient>();
1555#endif
1556 m_editorClient = makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::EditorClient>();
1557 m_formClient = makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::FormClient>();
1558 m_loaderClient = makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::PageLoaderClient>();
1559 m_policyClient.initialize(0);
1560 m_resourceLoadClient = makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::ResourceLoadClient>();
1561 m_uiClient = makeUnique<API::InjectedBundle::PageUIClient>();
1562#if ENABLE(FULLSCREEN_API)
1563 m_fullScreenClient.initialize(0);
1564#endif
1565
1566 m_printContext = nullptr;
1567 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().detachFromParent();
1568 m_drawingArea = nullptr;
1569
1570 DeferredPageDestructor::createDeferredPageDestructor(WTFMove(m_page), this);
1571
1572 bool isRunningModal = m_isRunningModal;
1573 m_isRunningModal = false;
1574
1575 auto& webProcess = WebProcess::singleton();
1576#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
1577 if (m_remoteObjectRegistry)
1578 m_remoteObjectRegistry->close();
1579 ASSERT(!m_remoteObjectRegistry);
1580#endif
1581#if ENABLE(SCROLLING_THREAD)
1582 if (m_useAsyncScrolling)
1583 webProcess.eventDispatcher().removeScrollingTreeForPage(this);
1584#endif
1585 webProcess.removeMessageReceiver(Messages::WebPage::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier);
1586 // FIXME: This should be done in the object destructors, and the objects themselves should be message receivers.
1587 webProcess.removeMessageReceiver(Messages::WebInspector::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier);
1588 webProcess.removeMessageReceiver(Messages::WebInspectorUI::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier);
1589 webProcess.removeMessageReceiver(Messages::RemoteWebInspectorUI::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier);
1590#if ENABLE(FULLSCREEN_API)
1591 webProcess.removeMessageReceiver(Messages::WebFullScreenManager::messageReceiverName(), m_identifier);
1592#endif
1593#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || PLATFORM(GTK)
1594 m_viewGestureGeometryCollector = nullptr;
1595#endif
1596
1597 // The WebPage can be destroyed by this call.
1598 WebProcess::singleton().removeWebPage(m_identifier);
1599
1600 WebProcess::singleton().updateActivePages(m_processDisplayName);
1601
1602 if (isRunningModal)
1603 RunLoop::main().stop();
1604}
1605
1606void WebPage::tryClose(CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
1607{
1608 bool shouldClose = corePage()->userInputBridge().tryClosePage();
1609 completionHandler(shouldClose);
1610}
1611
1612void WebPage::sendClose()
1613{
1614 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::ClosePage());
1615}
1616
1617void WebPage::suspendForProcessSwap()
1618{
1619 auto failedToSuspend = [this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] {
1620 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFailToSuspendAfterProcessSwap());
1621 };
1622
1623 auto* currentHistoryItem = m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().history().currentItem();
1624 if (!currentHistoryItem) {
1625 failedToSuspend();
1626 return;
1627 }
1628
1629 if (!BackForwardCache::singleton().addIfCacheable(*currentHistoryItem, corePage())) {
1630 failedToSuspend();
1631 return;
1632 }
1633
1634 // Back/forward cache does not break the opener link for the main frame (only does so for the subframes) because the
1635 // main frame is normally re-used for the navigation. However, in the case of process-swapping, the main frame
1636 // is now hosted in another process and the one in this process is in the cache.
1637 if (m_mainFrame->coreFrame())
1638 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().detachFromAllOpenedFrames();
1639
1640 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidSuspendAfterProcessSwap());
1641}

1643void WebPage::loadURLInFrame(URL&& url, const String& referrer, FrameIdentifier frameID)
1644{
1645 WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
1646 if (!frame)
1647 return;
1648
1649 frame->coreFrame()->loader().load(FrameLoadRequest(*frame->coreFrame(), ResourceRequest(url, referrer)));
1650}
1651
1652void WebPage::loadDataInFrame(IPC::DataReference&& data, String&& MIMEType, String&& encodingName, URL&& baseURL, FrameIdentifier frameID)
1653{
1654 auto* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
1655 if (!frame)
1656 return;
1657 ASSERT(&mainWebFrame() != frame);
1658
1659 auto sharedBuffer = SharedBuffer::create(data.data(), data.size());
1660 ResourceResponse response(baseURL, MIMEType, sharedBuffer->size(), encodingName);
1661 SubstituteData substituteData(WTFMove(sharedBuffer), baseURL, WTFMove(response), SubstituteData::SessionHistoryVisibility::Hidden);
1662 frame->coreFrame()->loader().load(FrameLoadRequest(*frame->coreFrame(), ResourceRequest(baseURL), WTFMove(substituteData)));
1663}

1667{
1668}
1669#endif
1670
1671void WebPage::loadRequest(LoadParameters&& loadParameters)
1672{
1673 setLastNavigationWasAppBound(loadParameters.request.isAppBound());
1674
1675#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
1676 setIsNavigatingToAppBoundDomain(loadParameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, &m_mainFrame.get());
1677#endif
1678
1679 SendStopResponsivenessTimer stopper;
1680
1681 m_pendingNavigationID = loadParameters.navigationID;
1682 m_pendingWebsitePolicies = WTFMove(loadParameters.websitePolicies);
1683
1684 m_sandboxExtensionTracker.beginLoad(m_mainFrame.ptr(), WTFMove(loadParameters.sandboxExtensionHandle));
1685
1686 // Let the InjectedBundle know we are about to start the load, passing the user data from the UIProcess
1687 // to all the client to set up any needed state.
1688 m_loaderClient->willLoadURLRequest(*this, loadParameters.request, WebProcess::singleton().transformHandlesToObjects(loadParameters.userData.object()).get());
1689
1690 platformDidReceiveLoadParameters(loadParameters);
1691
1692 // Initate the load in WebCore.
1693 FrameLoadRequest frameLoadRequest { *m_mainFrame->coreFrame(), loadParameters.request };
1694 frameLoadRequest.setShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy(loadParameters.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy);
1695 frameLoadRequest.setShouldTreatAsContinuingLoad(loadParameters.shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad);
1696 frameLoadRequest.setLockHistory(loadParameters.lockHistory);
1697 frameLoadRequest.setLockBackForwardList(loadParameters.lockBackForwardList);
1698 frameLoadRequest.setClientRedirectSourceForHistory(loadParameters.clientRedirectSourceForHistory);
1699 frameLoadRequest.setIsRequestFromClientOrUserInput();
1700
1701 corePage()->userInputBridge().loadRequest(WTFMove(frameLoadRequest));
1702
1703 ASSERT(!m_pendingNavigationID);
1704 ASSERT(!m_pendingWebsitePolicies);
1705}
1706
1707// LoadRequestWaitingForProcessLaunch should never be sent to the WebProcess. It must always be converted to a LoadRequest message.
1708NO_RETURN void WebPage::loadRequestWaitingForProcessLaunch(LoadParameters&&, URL&&, WebPageProxyIdentifier, bool)
1709{
1710 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1711}
1712
1713void WebPage::loadDataImpl(uint64_t navigationID, bool shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad, std::optional<WebsitePoliciesData>&& websitePolicies, Ref<SharedBuffer>&& sharedBuffer, const String& MIMEType, const String& encodingName, const URL& baseURL, const URL& unreachableURL, const UserData& userData, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, ShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy)
1714{
1715#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
1716 setIsNavigatingToAppBoundDomain(isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, &m_mainFrame.get());
1717#endif
1718
1719 SendStopResponsivenessTimer stopper;
1720
1721 m_pendingNavigationID = navigationID;
1722 m_pendingWebsitePolicies = WTFMove(websitePolicies);
1723
1724 ResourceRequest request(baseURL);
1725 ResourceResponse response(URL(), MIMEType, sharedBuffer->size(), encodingName);
1726 SubstituteData substituteData(WTFMove(sharedBuffer), unreachableURL, response, SubstituteData::SessionHistoryVisibility::Hidden);
1727
1728 // Let the InjectedBundle know we are about to start the load, passing the user data from the UIProcess
1729 // to all the client to set up any needed state.
1730 m_loaderClient->willLoadDataRequest(*this, request, const_cast<SharedBuffer*>(substituteData.content()), substituteData.mimeType(), substituteData.textEncoding(), substituteData.failingURL(), WebProcess::singleton().transformHandlesToObjects(userData.object()).get());
1731
1732 // Initate the load in WebCore.
1733 FrameLoadRequest frameLoadRequest(*m_mainFrame->coreFrame(), request, substituteData);
1734 frameLoadRequest.setShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy(shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy);
1735 frameLoadRequest.setShouldTreatAsContinuingLoad(shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad);
1736 frameLoadRequest.setIsRequestFromClientOrUserInput();
1737 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().load(WTFMove(frameLoadRequest));
1738}
1739
1740void WebPage::loadData(LoadParameters&& loadParameters)
1741{
1742 platformDidReceiveLoadParameters(loadParameters);
1743
1744 auto sharedBuffer = SharedBuffer::create(loadParameters.data.data(), loadParameters.data.size());
1745
1746 URL baseURL;
1747 if (loadParameters.baseURLString.isEmpty())
1748 baseURL = aboutBlankURL();
1749 else {
1750 baseURL = URL(URL(), loadParameters.baseURLString);
1751 if (baseURL.isValid()) {
1752 if (!baseURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily())
1753 LegacySchemeRegistry::registerURLSchemeAsHandledBySchemeHandler(baseURL.protocol().toString());
1754 } else
1755 baseURL = aboutBlankURL();
1756 }
1757
1758 loadDataImpl(loadParameters.navigationID, loadParameters.shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad, WTFMove(loadParameters.websitePolicies), WTFMove(sharedBuffer), loadParameters.MIMEType, loadParameters.encodingName, baseURL, URL(), loadParameters.userData, loadParameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, loadParameters.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy);
1759}
1760
1761void WebPage::loadAlternateHTML(LoadParameters&& loadParameters)
1762{
1763 platformDidReceiveLoadParameters(loadParameters);
1764
1765 URL baseURL = loadParameters.baseURLString.isEmpty() ? aboutBlankURL() : URL(URL(), loadParameters.baseURLString);
1766 URL unreachableURL = loadParameters.unreachableURLString.isEmpty() ? URL() : URL(URL(), loadParameters.unreachableURLString);
1767 URL provisionalLoadErrorURL = loadParameters.provisionalLoadErrorURLString.isEmpty() ? URL() : URL(URL(), loadParameters.provisionalLoadErrorURLString);
1768 auto sharedBuffer = SharedBuffer::create(loadParameters.data.data(), loadParameters.data.size());
1769 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().setProvisionalLoadErrorBeingHandledURL(provisionalLoadErrorURL);
1770 loadDataImpl(loadParameters.navigationID, loadParameters.shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad, WTFMove(loadParameters.websitePolicies), WTFMove(sharedBuffer), loadParameters.MIMEType, loadParameters.encodingName, baseURL, unreachableURL, loadParameters.userData, loadParameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain);
1771 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().setProvisionalLoadErrorBeingHandledURL({ });
1772}
1773
1774void WebPage::loadSimulatedRequestAndResponse(LoadParameters&& loadParameters, ResourceResponse&& simulatedResponse)
1775{
1776 ASSERT(simulatedResponse.url() == loadParameters.request.url());
1777 ASSERT(simulatedResponse.mimeType() == loadParameters.MIMEType);
1778 ASSERT(simulatedResponse.textEncodingName() == loadParameters.encodingName);
1779 ASSERT(static_cast<size_t>(simulatedResponse.expectedContentLength()) == loadParameters.data.size());
1780
1781 setLastNavigationWasAppBound(loadParameters.request.isAppBound());
1782
1783 platformDidReceiveLoadParameters(loadParameters);
1784
1785 auto sharedBuffer = SharedBuffer::create(loadParameters.data.data(), loadParameters.data.size());
1786
1787#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
1788 setIsNavigatingToAppBoundDomain(loadParameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, &m_mainFrame.get());
1789#endif
1790
1791 SendStopResponsivenessTimer stopper;
1792
1793 m_pendingNavigationID = loadParameters.navigationID;
1794 m_pendingWebsitePolicies = WTFMove(loadParameters.websitePolicies);
1795
1796 SubstituteData substituteData(WTFMove(sharedBuffer), loadParameters.request.url(), simulatedResponse, SubstituteData::SessionHistoryVisibility::Visible);
1797
1798 // Let the InjectedBundle know we are about to start the load, passing the user data from the UIProcess
1799 // to all the client to set up any needed state.
1800 m_loaderClient->willLoadDataRequest(*this, loadParameters.request, const_cast<SharedBuffer*>(substituteData.content()), substituteData.mimeType(), substituteData.textEncoding(), substituteData.failingURL(), WebProcess::singleton().transformHandlesToObjects(loadParameters.userData.object()).get());
1801
1802 // Initate the load in WebCore.
1803 FrameLoadRequest frameLoadRequest(*m_mainFrame->coreFrame(), loadParameters.request, substituteData);
1804 frameLoadRequest.setShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy(loadParameters.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy);
1805 frameLoadRequest.setShouldTreatAsContinuingLoad(loadParameters.shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad);
1806 frameLoadRequest.setLockHistory(loadParameters.lockHistory);
1807 frameLoadRequest.setLockBackForwardList(loadParameters.lockBackForwardList);
1808 frameLoadRequest.setClientRedirectSourceForHistory(loadParameters.clientRedirectSourceForHistory);
1809 frameLoadRequest.setIsRequestFromClientOrUserInput();
1810
1811 // FIXME: Should this be "corePage()->userInputBridge().loadRequest(WTFMove(frameLoadRequest));"?
1812 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().load(WTFMove(frameLoadRequest));
1813}
1814
1815void WebPage::navigateToPDFLinkWithSimulatedClick(const String& url, IntPoint documentPoint, IntPoint screenPoint)
1816{
1817 Frame* mainFrame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame();
1818 Document* mainFrameDocument = mainFrame->document();
1819 if (!mainFrameDocument)
1820 return;
1821
1822 const int singleClick = 1;
1823 // FIXME: Set modifier keys.
1824 // FIXME: This should probably set IsSimulated::Yes.
1825 auto mouseEvent = MouseEvent::create(eventNames().clickEvent, Event::CanBubble::Yes, Event::IsCancelable::Yes, Event::IsComposed::Yes,
1826 MonotonicTime::now(), nullptr, singleClick, screenPoint, documentPoint, { }, { }, 0, 0, nullptr, 0, WebCore::NoTap);
1827
1828 mainFrame->loader().changeLocation(mainFrameDocument->completeURL(url), emptyString(), mouseEvent.ptr(), ReferrerPolicy::NoReferrer, ShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy::ShouldNotAllow);
1829}
1830
1831void WebPage::stopLoadingFrame(FrameIdentifier frameID)
1832{
1833 WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
1834 if (!frame)
1835 return;
1836
1837 auto* coreFrame = frame->coreFrame();
1838 if (!coreFrame || !m_page)
1839 return;
1840
1841 m_page->userInputBridge().stopLoadingFrame(*coreFrame);
1842}
1843
1844void WebPage::stopLoading()
1845{
1846 if (!m_page || !m_mainFrame->coreFrame())
1847 return;
1848
1849 SendStopResponsivenessTimer stopper;
1850 m_page->userInputBridge().stopLoadingFrame(*m_mainFrame->coreFrame());
1851}
1852
1853bool WebPage::defersLoading() const
1854{
1855 return m_page->defersLoading();
1856}
1857
1858void WebPage::setDefersLoading(bool defersLoading)
1859{
1860 m_page->setDefersLoading(defersLoading);
1861}
1862
1863void WebPage::reload(uint64_t navigationID, uint32_t reloadOptions, SandboxExtension::Handle&& sandboxExtensionHandle)
1864{
1865 SendStopResponsivenessTimer stopper;
1866
1867 ASSERT(!m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->loader().frameHasLoaded() || !m_pendingNavigationID);
1868 m_pendingNavigationID = navigationID;
1869
1870 m_sandboxExtensionTracker.beginReload(m_mainFrame.ptr(), WTFMove(sandboxExtensionHandle));
1871 if (m_page && m_mainFrame->coreFrame())
1872 m_page->userInputBridge().reloadFrame(*m_mainFrame->coreFrame(), OptionSet<ReloadOption>::fromRaw(reloadOptions));
1873 else
1874 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1875
1876 if (m_pendingNavigationID) {
1877 // This can happen if FrameLoader::reload() returns early because the document URL is empty.
1878 // The reload does nothing so we need to reset the pending navigation. See webkit.org/b/153210.
1879 m_pendingNavigationID = 0;
1880 }
1881}
1882
1883void WebPage::goToBackForwardItem(uint64_t navigationID, const BackForwardItemIdentifier& backForwardItemID, FrameLoadType backForwardType, ShouldTreatAsContinuingLoad shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad, std::optional<WebsitePoliciesData>&& websitePolicies)
1884{
1885 SendStopResponsivenessTimer stopper;
1886
1887 ASSERT(isBackForwardLoadType(backForwardType));
1888
1889 HistoryItem* item = WebBackForwardListProxy::itemForID(backForwardItemID);
1890 ASSERT(item);
1891 if (!item)
1892 return;
1893
1894 LOG(Loading, "In WebProcess pid %i, WebPage %" PRIu64 " is navigating to back/forward URL %s", getCurrentProcessID(), m_identifier.toUInt64(), item->url().string().utf8().data());
1895
1896 ASSERT(!m_pendingNavigationID);
1897 m_pendingNavigationID = navigationID;
1898 m_pendingWebsitePolicies = WTFMove(websitePolicies);
1899
1900 m_page->goToItem(*item, backForwardType, shouldTreatAsContinuingLoad);
1901}

1905 m_page->mainFrame().loader().history().restoreScrollPositionAndViewState();
1906}

1912
1913static std::optional<FrameTreeNodeData> frameTreeNodeData(Frame& frame)
1914{
1915 std::optional<FrameTreeNodeData> info;
1916 if (auto* webFrame = WebFrame::fromCoreFrame(frame)) {
1917 Vector<FrameTreeNodeData> children;
1918 for (auto* childFrame = frame.tree().firstChild(); childFrame; childFrame = childFrame->tree().nextSibling()) {
1919 if (auto childInfo = frameTreeNodeData(*childFrame))
1920 children.append(WTFMove(*childInfo));
1921 }
1922 info = FrameTreeNodeData {
1923 webFrame->info(),
1924 WTFMove(children)
1925 };
1926 }
1927 return info;
1928}
1929
1930void WebPage::getAllFrames(CompletionHandler<void(FrameTreeNodeData&&)>&& completionHandler)
1931{
1932 completionHandler(*frameTreeNodeData(m_page->mainFrame()));
1933}
1934
1935void WebPage::setSize(const WebCore::IntSize& viewSize)
1936{
1937 if (m_viewSize == viewSize)
1938 return;
1939
1940 m_viewSize = viewSize;
1941 FrameView* view = m_page->mainFrame().view();
1942 view->resize(viewSize);
1943 m_drawingArea->setNeedsDisplay();
1944
1945#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS)
1946 if (view->useFixedLayout())
1947 sendViewportAttributesChanged(m_page->viewportArguments());
1948#endif
1949}
1950
1951#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS)
1952void WebPage::sendViewportAttributesChanged(const ViewportArguments& viewportArguments)
1953{
1954 FrameView* view = m_page->mainFrame().view();
1955 ASSERT(view && view->useFixedLayout());
1956
1957 // Viewport properties have no impact on zero sized fixed viewports.
1958 if (m_viewSize.isEmpty())
1959 return;
1960
1961 // Recalculate the recommended layout size, when the available size (device pixel) changes.
1962 Settings& settings = m_page->settings();
1963
1964 int minimumLayoutFallbackWidth = std::max<int>(settings.layoutFallbackWidth(), m_viewSize.width());
1965
1966 // If unset we use the viewport dimensions. This fits with the behavior of desktop browsers.
1967 int deviceWidth = (settings.deviceWidth() > 0) ? settings.deviceWidth() : m_viewSize.width();
1968 int deviceHeight = (settings.deviceHeight() > 0) ? settings.deviceHeight() : m_viewSize.height();
1969
1970 ViewportAttributes attr = computeViewportAttributes(viewportArguments, minimumLayoutFallbackWidth, deviceWidth, deviceHeight, 1, m_viewSize);
1971
1972 // If no layout was done yet set contentFixedOrigin to (0,0).
1973 IntPoint contentFixedOrigin = view->didFirstLayout() ? view->fixedVisibleContentRect().location() : IntPoint();
1974
1975 // Put the width and height to the viewport width and height. In css units however.
1976 // Use FloatSize to avoid truncated values during scale.
1977 FloatSize contentFixedSize = m_viewSize;
1978
1979 contentFixedSize.scale(1 / attr.initialScale);
1980 view->setFixedVisibleContentRect(IntRect(contentFixedOrigin, roundedIntSize(contentFixedSize)));
1981
1982 attr.initialScale = m_page->viewportArguments().zoom; // Resets auto (-1) if no value was set by user.
1983
1984 // This also takes care of the relayout.
1985 setFixedLayoutSize(roundedIntSize(attr.layoutSize));
1986
1987#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS)
1988 m_drawingArea->didChangeViewportAttributes(WTFMove(attr));
1989#else
1990 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidChangeViewportProperties(attr));
1991#endif
1992}
1993#endif
1994
1995void WebPage::scrollMainFrameIfNotAtMaxScrollPosition(const IntSize& scrollOffset)
1996{
1997 FrameView* frameView = m_page->mainFrame().view();
1998
1999 ScrollPosition scrollPosition = frameView->scrollPosition();
2000 ScrollPosition maximumScrollPosition = frameView->maximumScrollPosition();
2001
2002 // If the current scroll position in a direction is the max scroll position
2003 // we don't want to scroll at all.
2004 IntSize newScrollOffset;
2005 if (scrollPosition.x() < maximumScrollPosition.x())
2006 newScrollOffset.setWidth(scrollOffset.width());
2007 if (scrollPosition.y() < maximumScrollPosition.y())
2008 newScrollOffset.setHeight(scrollOffset.height());
2009
2010 if (newScrollOffset.isZero())
2011 return;
2012
2013 frameView->setScrollPosition(frameView->scrollPosition() + newScrollOffset);
2014}
2015
2016void WebPage::drawRect(GraphicsContext& graphicsContext, const IntRect& rect)
2017{
2018#if PLATFORM(MAC)
2019 FrameView* mainFrameView = m_page->mainFrame().view();
2020 LocalDefaultSystemAppearance localAppearance(mainFrameView ? mainFrameView->useDarkAppearance() : false);
2021#endif
2022
2023 GraphicsContextStateSaver stateSaver(graphicsContext);
2024 graphicsContext.clip(rect);
2025
2026 m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->view()->paint(graphicsContext, rect);
2027
2028#if PLATFORM(GTK) || PLATFORM(WIN) || PLATFORM(PLAYSTATION)
2029 if (!m_page->settings().acceleratedCompositingEnabled() && m_page->inspectorController().enabled() && m_page->inspectorController().shouldShowOverlay()) {
2030 graphicsContext.beginTransparencyLayer(1);
2031 m_page->inspectorController().drawHighlight(graphicsContext);
2032 graphicsContext.endTransparencyLayer();
2033 }
2034#endif
2035}

2037double WebPage::textZoomFactor() const
2038{

2040 if (pluginView && pluginView->requiresUnifiedScaleFactor()) {
2041 if (pluginView->handlesPageScaleFactor())
2042 return pluginView->pageScaleFactor();
2043 return pageScaleFactor();
2044 }
2045
2046 Frame* frame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame();
2047 if (!frame)
2048 return 1;
2049 return frame->textZoomFactor();
2050}

2052void WebPage::setTextZoomFactor(double zoomFactor)
2053{

2055 if (pluginView && pluginView->requiresUnifiedScaleFactor()) {
2056 if (pluginView->handlesPageScaleFactor())
2057 pluginView->setPageScaleFactor(zoomFactor, IntPoint());
2058 else
2059 scalePage(zoomFactor, IntPoint());
2060 return;
2061 }
2062
2063 Frame* frame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame();
2064 if (!frame)
2065 return;
2066 frame->setTextZoomFactor(static_cast<float>(zoomFactor));
2067}

2101static void dumpHistoryItem(HistoryItem& item, size_t indent, bool isCurrentItem, StringBuilder& stringBuilder, const String& directoryName)
2102{
2103 if (isCurrentItem)
2104 stringBuilder.append("curr-> ");
2105 else {
2106 for (size_t i = 0; i < indent; ++i)
2107 stringBuilder.append(' ');
2108 }
2109
2110 auto url = item.url();
2111 if (url.protocolIs("file")) {
2112 size_t start = url.string().find(directoryName);
2113 if (start == WTF::notFound)
2114 start = 0;
2115 else
2116 start += directoryName.length();
2117 stringBuilder.append("(file test):", StringView { url.string() }.substring(start));
2118 } else
2119 stringBuilder.append(url.string());
2120
2121 auto& target = item.target();
2122 if (target.length())
2123 stringBuilder.append(" (in frame \"", target, "\")");
2124
2125 if (item.isTargetItem())
2126 stringBuilder.append(" **nav target**");
2127
2128 stringBuilder.append('\n');
2129
2130 Vector<Ref<HistoryItem>> children;
2131 children.reserveInitialCapacity(item.children().size());
2132 for (auto& child : item.children())
2133 children.uncheckedAppend(child.copyRef());
2134 std::stable_sort(children.begin(), children.end(), [] (auto& a, auto& b) {
2135 return codePointCompare(a->target(), b->target()) < 0;
2136 });
2137 for (auto& child : children)
2138 dumpHistoryItem(child, indent + 4, false, stringBuilder, directoryName);
2139}
2140
2141String WebPage::dumpHistoryForTesting(const String& directory)
2142{
2143 if (!m_page)
2144 return { };
2145
2146 auto& list = m_page->backForward();
2147
2148 StringBuilder builder;
2149 int begin = -list.backCount();
2150 if (list.itemAtIndex(begin)->url() == aboutBlankURL())
2151 ++begin;
2152 for (int i = begin; i <= static_cast<int>(list.forwardCount()); ++i)
2153 dumpHistoryItem(*list.itemAtIndex(i), 8, !i, builder, directory);
2154 return builder.toString();
2155}

2190
2191void WebPage::scalePage(double scale, const IntPoint& origin)
2192{
2193 double totalScale = scale * viewScaleFactor();
2194 bool willChangeScaleFactor = totalScale != totalScaleFactor();
2195
2196#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
2197 if (willChangeScaleFactor) {
2198 if (!m_inDynamicSizeUpdate)
2199 m_dynamicSizeUpdateHistory.clear();
2200 m_scaleWasSetByUIProcess = false;
2201 }
2202#endif
2203 PluginView* pluginView = pluginViewForFrame(&m_page->mainFrame());
2204 if (pluginView && pluginView->handlesPageScaleFactor()) {
2205 // If the main-frame plugin wants to handle the page scale factor, make sure to reset WebCore's page scale.
2206 // Otherwise, we can end up with an immutable but non-1 page scale applied by WebCore on top of whatever the plugin does.
2207 if (m_page->pageScaleFactor() != 1) {
2208 m_page->setPageScaleFactor(1, origin);
2209 for (auto* pluginView : m_pluginViews)
2210 pluginView->pageScaleFactorDidChange();
2211 }
2212
2213 pluginView->setPageScaleFactor(totalScale, origin);
2214 return;
2215 }
2216
2217 m_page->setPageScaleFactor(totalScale, origin);
2218
2219 // We can't early return before setPageScaleFactor because the origin might be different.
2220 if (!willChangeScaleFactor)
2221 return;
2222
2223 for (auto* pluginView : m_pluginViews)
2224 pluginView->pageScaleFactorDidChange();
2225
2226#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS) || USE(TEXTURE_MAPPER)
2227 m_drawingArea->deviceOrPageScaleFactorChanged();
2228#endif
2229
2230 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::PageScaleFactorDidChange(scale));
2231 platformDidScalePage();
2232}
2233
2234#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
2235
2236void WebPage::platformDidScalePage()
2237{
2238}
2239
2240#endif
2241
2242void WebPage::scalePageInViewCoordinates(double scale, IntPoint centerInViewCoordinates)
2243{
2244 double totalScale = scale * viewScaleFactor();
2245 if (totalScale == totalScaleFactor())
2246 return;
2247
2248 IntPoint scrollPositionAtNewScale = mainFrameView()->rootViewToContents(-centerInViewCoordinates);
2249 double scaleRatio = scale / pageScaleFactor();
2250 scrollPositionAtNewScale.scale(scaleRatio);
2251 scalePage(scale, scrollPositionAtNewScale);
2252}
2253
2254double WebPage::totalScaleFactor() const
2255{
2256 PluginView* pluginView = pluginViewForFrame(&m_page->mainFrame());
2257 if (pluginView && pluginView->handlesPageScaleFactor())
2258 return pluginView->pageScaleFactor();
2259
2260 return m_page->pageScaleFactor();
2261}
2262
2263double WebPage::pageScaleFactor() const
2264{
2265 return totalScaleFactor() / viewScaleFactor();
2266}
2267
2268double WebPage::viewScaleFactor() const
2269{
2270 return m_page->viewScaleFactor();
2271}
2272
2273void WebPage::scaleView(double scale)
2274{
2275 if (viewScaleFactor() == scale)
2276 return;
2277
2278 float pageScale = pageScaleFactor();
2279
2280 IntPoint scrollPositionAtNewScale;
2281 if (FrameView* mainFrameView = m_page->mainFrame().view()) {
2282 double scaleRatio = scale / viewScaleFactor();
2283 scrollPositionAtNewScale = mainFrameView->scrollPosition();
2284 scrollPositionAtNewScale.scale(scaleRatio);
2285 }
2286
2287 m_page->setViewScaleFactor(scale);
2288 scalePage(pageScale, scrollPositionAtNewScale);
2289}
2290
2291void WebPage::setDeviceScaleFactor(float scaleFactor)
2292{
2293 if (scaleFactor == m_page->deviceScaleFactor())
2294 return;
2295
2296 m_page->setDeviceScaleFactor(scaleFactor);
2297
2298 // Tell all our plug-in views that the device scale factor changed.
2299#if PLATFORM(MAC)
2300 for (auto* pluginView : m_pluginViews)
2301 pluginView->setDeviceScaleFactor(scaleFactor);
2302
2303 updateHeaderAndFooterLayersForDeviceScaleChange(scaleFactor);
2304#endif
2305
2306 if (findController().isShowingOverlay()) {
2307 // We must have updated layout to get the selection rects right.
2308 layoutIfNeeded();
2309 findController().deviceScaleFactorDidChange();
2310 }
2311
2312#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS) || USE(TEXTURE_MAPPER)
2313 m_drawingArea->deviceOrPageScaleFactorChanged();
2314#endif
2315}
2316
2317float WebPage::deviceScaleFactor() const
2318{
2319 return m_page->deviceScaleFactor();
2320}

2332void WebPage::setUseFixedLayout(bool fixed)
2333{

2335 if (m_useFixedLayout == fixed)
2336 return;

2338

2345 return;

2352}

2355{

2357 if (!view || view->fixedLayoutSize() == size)

2361 view->setFixedLayoutSize(size);
2362
2363 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::FixedLayoutSizeDidChange(size));
2364 return true;
2365}

2543void WebPage::takeSnapshot(IntRect snapshotRect, IntSize bitmapSize, uint32_t options, CompletionHandler<void(const WebKit::ShareableBitmap::Handle&)>&& completionHandler)
2544{
2545 SnapshotOptions snapshotOptions = static_cast<SnapshotOptions>(options);
2546 snapshotOptions |= SnapshotOptionsShareable;
2547
2548 RefPtr<WebImage> image = snapshotAtSize(snapshotRect, bitmapSize, snapshotOptions);
2549
2550 ShareableBitmap::Handle handle;
2551 if (image)
2552 image->bitmap().createHandle(handle, SharedMemory::Protection::ReadOnly);
2553
2554 completionHandler(handle);
2555}
2556
2557RefPtr<WebImage> WebPage::scaledSnapshotWithOptions(const IntRect& rect, double additionalScaleFactor, SnapshotOptions options)
2558{
2559 IntRect snapshotRect = rect;
2560 IntSize bitmapSize = snapshotRect.size();
2561 if (options & SnapshotOptionsPrinting) {
2562 ASSERT(additionalScaleFactor == 1);
2563 Frame* coreFrame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame();
2564 if (!coreFrame)
2565 return nullptr;
2566 bitmapSize.setHeight(PrintContext::numberOfPages(*coreFrame, bitmapSize) * (bitmapSize.height() + 1) - 1);
2567 } else {
2568 double scaleFactor = additionalScaleFactor;
2569 if (!(options & SnapshotOptionsExcludeDeviceScaleFactor))
2570 scaleFactor *= corePage()->deviceScaleFactor();
2571 bitmapSize.scale(scaleFactor);
2572 }
2573
2574 return snapshotAtSize(rect, bitmapSize, options);
2575}
2576
2577void WebPage::paintSnapshotAtSize(const IntRect& rect, const IntSize& bitmapSize, SnapshotOptions options, Frame& frame, FrameView& frameView, GraphicsContext& graphicsContext)
2578{
2579 TraceScope snapshotScope(PaintSnapshotStart, PaintSnapshotEnd, options);
2580
2581 IntRect snapshotRect = rect;
2582 float horizontalScaleFactor = static_cast<float>(bitmapSize.width()) / rect.width();
2583 float verticalScaleFactor = static_cast<float>(bitmapSize.height()) / rect.height();
2584 float scaleFactor = std::max(horizontalScaleFactor, verticalScaleFactor);
2585
2586 if (options & SnapshotOptionsPrinting) {
2587 PrintContext::spoolAllPagesWithBoundaries(frame, graphicsContext, snapshotRect.size());
2588 return;
2589 }
2590
2591 Color documentBackgroundColor = frameView.documentBackgroundColor();
2592 Color backgroundColor = (frame.settings().backgroundShouldExtendBeyondPage() && documentBackgroundColor.isValid()) ? documentBackgroundColor : frameView.baseBackgroundColor();
2593 graphicsContext.fillRect(IntRect(IntPoint(), bitmapSize), backgroundColor);
2594
2595 if (!(options & SnapshotOptionsExcludeDeviceScaleFactor)) {
2596 double deviceScaleFactor = frame.page()->deviceScaleFactor();
2597 graphicsContext.applyDeviceScaleFactor(deviceScaleFactor);
2598 scaleFactor /= deviceScaleFactor;
2599 }
2600
2601 graphicsContext.scale(scaleFactor);
2602 graphicsContext.translate(-snapshotRect.location());
2603
2604 FrameView::SelectionInSnapshot shouldPaintSelection = FrameView::IncludeSelection;
2605 if (options & SnapshotOptionsExcludeSelectionHighlighting)
2606 shouldPaintSelection = FrameView::ExcludeSelection;
2607
2608 FrameView::CoordinateSpaceForSnapshot coordinateSpace = FrameView::DocumentCoordinates;
2609 if (options & SnapshotOptionsInViewCoordinates)
2610 coordinateSpace = FrameView::ViewCoordinates;
2611
2612 frameView.paintContentsForSnapshot(graphicsContext, snapshotRect, shouldPaintSelection, coordinateSpace);
2613
2614 if (options & SnapshotOptionsPaintSelectionRectangle) {
2615 FloatRect selectionRectangle = frame.selection().selectionBounds();
2616 graphicsContext.setStrokeColor(Color::red);
2617 graphicsContext.strokeRect(selectionRectangle, 1);
2618 }
2619}
2620
2621static ShareableBitmap::Configuration snapshotOptionsToBitmapConfiguration(SnapshotOptions options, WebPage& page)
2622{
2623 ShareableBitmap::Configuration configuration;
2624#if USE(CG)
2625 if (options & SnapshotOptionsUseScreenColorSpace)
2626 configuration.colorSpace = screenColorSpace(page.corePage()->mainFrame().view());
2627#endif
2628 return configuration;
2629}
2630
2631RefPtr<WebImage> WebPage::snapshotAtSize(const IntRect& rect, const IntSize& bitmapSize, SnapshotOptions options)
2632{
2633 Frame* coreFrame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame();
2634 if (!coreFrame)
2635 return nullptr;
2636
2637 FrameView* frameView = coreFrame->view();
2638 if (!frameView)
2639 return nullptr;
2640
2641 auto snapshot = WebImage::create(bitmapSize, snapshotOptionsToImageOptions(options), snapshotOptionsToBitmapConfiguration(options, *this));
2642 if (!snapshot)
2643 return nullptr;
2644 auto graphicsContext = snapshot->bitmap().createGraphicsContext();
2645 if (!graphicsContext)
2646 return nullptr;
2647
2648 paintSnapshotAtSize(rect, bitmapSize, options, *coreFrame, *frameView, *graphicsContext);
2649
2650 return snapshot;
2651}
2652
2653RefPtr<WebImage> WebPage::snapshotNode(WebCore::Node& node, SnapshotOptions options, unsigned maximumPixelCount)
2654{
2655 Frame* coreFrame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame();
2656 if (!coreFrame)
2657 return nullptr;
2658
2659 FrameView* frameView = coreFrame->view();
2660 if (!frameView)
2661 return nullptr;
2662
2663 if (!node.renderer())
2664 return nullptr;
2665
2666 LayoutRect topLevelRect;
2667 IntRect snapshotRect = snappedIntRect(node.renderer()->paintingRootRect(topLevelRect));
2668 if (snapshotRect.isEmpty())
2669 return nullptr;
2670
2671 double scaleFactor = 1;
2672 IntSize snapshotSize = snapshotRect.size();
2673 unsigned maximumHeight = maximumPixelCount / snapshotSize.width();
2674 if (maximumHeight < static_cast<unsigned>(snapshotSize.height())) {
2675 scaleFactor = static_cast<double>(maximumHeight) / snapshotSize.height();
2676 snapshotSize = IntSize(snapshotSize.width() * scaleFactor, maximumHeight);
2677 }
2678
2679 auto snapshot = WebImage::create(snapshotSize, snapshotOptionsToImageOptions(options), snapshotOptionsToBitmapConfiguration(options, *this));
2680 if (!snapshot)
2681 return nullptr;
2682 auto graphicsContext = snapshot->bitmap().createGraphicsContext();
2683 if (!graphicsContext)
2684 return nullptr;
2685
2686 if (!(options & SnapshotOptionsExcludeDeviceScaleFactor)) {
2687 double deviceScaleFactor = corePage()->deviceScaleFactor();
2688 graphicsContext->applyDeviceScaleFactor(deviceScaleFactor);
2689 scaleFactor /= deviceScaleFactor;
2690 }
2691
2692 graphicsContext->scale(scaleFactor);
2693 graphicsContext->translate(-snapshotRect.location());
2694
2695 Color savedBackgroundColor = frameView->baseBackgroundColor();
2696 frameView->setBaseBackgroundColor(Color::transparentBlack);
2697 frameView->setNodeToDraw(&node);
2698
2699 frameView->paintContentsForSnapshot(*graphicsContext, snapshotRect, FrameView::ExcludeSelection, FrameView::DocumentCoordinates);
2700
2701 frameView->setBaseBackgroundColor(savedBackgroundColor);
2702 frameView->setNodeToDraw(nullptr);
2703
2704 return snapshot;
2705}

2736WebContextMenu* WebPage::contextMenuAtPointInWindow(const IntPoint& point)
2737{
2738 corePage()->contextMenuController().clearContextMenu();
2739
2740 // Simulate a mouse click to generate the correct menu.
2741 PlatformMouseEvent mousePressEvent(point, point, RightButton, PlatformEvent::MousePressed, 1, false, false, false, false, WallTime::now(), WebCore::ForceAtClick, WebCore::NoTap);
2742 corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMousePressEvent(mousePressEvent);
2743 bool handled = corePage()->userInputBridge().handleContextMenuEvent(mousePressEvent, corePage()->mainFrame());
2744 auto* menu = handled ? &contextMenu() : nullptr;
2745 PlatformMouseEvent mouseReleaseEvent(point, point, RightButton, PlatformEvent::MouseReleased, 1, false, false, false, false, WallTime::now(), WebCore::ForceAtClick, WebCore::NoTap);
2746 corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMouseReleaseEvent(mouseReleaseEvent);
2747
2748 return menu;
2749}

2764void WebPage::freezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason reason)
2765{
2766 auto oldReasons = m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.toRaw();
2767 UNUSED_PARAM(oldReasons);
2768 m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.add(reason);
2769 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSuspension, "freezeLayerTree: Adding a reason to freeze layer tree (reason=%d, new=%d, old=%d)", static_cast<unsigned>(reason), m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.toRaw(), oldReasons);
2770 updateDrawingAreaLayerTreeFreezeState();
2771}
2772
2773void WebPage::unfreezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason reason)
2774{
2775 auto oldReasons = m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.toRaw();
2776 UNUSED_PARAM(oldReasons);
2777 m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.remove(reason);
2778 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSuspension, "unfreezeLayerTree: Removing a reason to freeze layer tree (reason=%d, new=%d, old=%d)", static_cast<unsigned>(reason), m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.toRaw(), oldReasons);
2779 updateDrawingAreaLayerTreeFreezeState();
2780}
2781
2782void WebPage::updateDrawingAreaLayerTreeFreezeState()
2783{
2784 if (!m_drawingArea)
2785 return;
2786
2787#if ENABLE(VIDEO_PRESENTATION_MODE)
2788 // When the browser is in the background, we should not freeze the layer tree
2789 // if the page has a video playing in picture-in-picture.
2790 if (m_videoFullscreenManager && m_videoFullscreenManager->hasVideoPlayingInPictureInPicture() && m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.hasExactlyOneBitSet() && m_layerTreeFreezeReasons.contains(LayerTreeFreezeReason::BackgroundApplication)) {
2791 m_drawingArea->setLayerTreeStateIsFrozen(false);
2792 return;
2793 }
2794#endif
2795
2796 m_drawingArea->setLayerTreeStateIsFrozen(!!m_layerTreeFreezeReasons);
2797}
2798
2799void WebPage::callVolatilityCompletionHandlers(bool succeeded)
2800{
2801 auto completionHandlers = std::exchange(m_markLayersAsVolatileCompletionHandlers, { });
2802 for (auto& completionHandler : completionHandlers)
2803 completionHandler(succeeded);
2804}
2805
2806void WebPage::layerVolatilityTimerFired()
2807{
2808 Seconds newInterval = m_layerVolatilityTimer.repeatInterval() * 2.;
2809 bool didSucceed = markLayersVolatileImmediatelyIfPossible();
2810 if (didSucceed || newInterval > maximumLayerVolatilityTimerInterval) {
2811 m_layerVolatilityTimer.stop();
2812 if (didSucceed)
2813 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "layerVolatilityTimerFired: Succeeded in marking layers as volatile");
2814 else
2815 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "layerVolatilityTimerFired: Failed to mark layers as volatile within %gms", maximumLayerVolatilityTimerInterval.milliseconds());
2816 callVolatilityCompletionHandlers(didSucceed);
2817 return;
2818 }
2819
2820 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Layers, "layerVolatilityTimerFired: Failed to mark all layers as volatile, will retry in %g ms", newInterval.milliseconds());
2821 m_layerVolatilityTimer.startRepeating(newInterval);
2822}
2823
2824bool WebPage::markLayersVolatileImmediatelyIfPossible()
2825{
2826 return !drawingArea() || drawingArea()->markLayersVolatileImmediatelyIfPossible();
2827}
2828
2829void WebPage::markLayersVolatile(CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
2830{
2831 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "markLayersVolatile:");
2832
2833 if (m_layerVolatilityTimer.isActive())
2834 m_layerVolatilityTimer.stop();
2835
2836 if (completionHandler)
2837 m_markLayersAsVolatileCompletionHandlers.append(WTFMove(completionHandler));
2838
2839 bool didSucceed = markLayersVolatileImmediatelyIfPossible();
2840 if (didSucceed || m_isSuspendedUnderLock) {
2841 if (didSucceed)
2842 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "markLayersVolatile: Successfully marked layers as volatile");
2843 else {
2844 // If we get suspended when locking the screen, it is expected that some IOSurfaces cannot be marked as purgeable so we do not keep retrying.
2845 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "markLayersVolatile: Did what we could to mark IOSurfaces as purgeable after locking the screen");
2846 }
2847 callVolatilityCompletionHandlers(didSucceed);
2848 return;
2849 }
2850
2851 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "markLayersVolatile: Failed to mark all layers as volatile, will retry in %g ms", initialLayerVolatilityTimerInterval.milliseconds());
2852 m_layerVolatilityTimer.startRepeating(initialLayerVolatilityTimerInterval);
2853}
2854
2855void WebPage::cancelMarkLayersVolatile()
2856{
2857 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "cancelMarkLayersVolatile:");
2858 m_layerVolatilityTimer.stop();
2859 callVolatilityCompletionHandlers(false);
2860}

2862class CurrentEvent {
2863public:
2864 explicit CurrentEvent(const WebEvent& event)
2865 : m_previousCurrentEvent(g_currentEvent)
2866 {
2867 g_currentEvent = &event;
2868 }
2869
2870 ~CurrentEvent()
2871 {
2872 g_currentEvent = m_previousCurrentEvent;
2873 }
2874
2875private:
2876 const WebEvent* m_previousCurrentEvent;
2877};
