2879#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENU_EVENT)
2880static bool isContextClick(const PlatformMouseEvent& event)
2881{
2882#if USE(APPKIT)
2883 return WebEventFactory::shouldBeHandledAsContextClick(event);
2884#else
2885 return event.button() == WebCore::RightButton;
2886#endif
2887}
2888
2889static bool handleContextMenuEvent(const PlatformMouseEvent& platformMouseEvent, WebPage* page)
2890{
2891 IntPoint point = page->corePage()->mainFrame().view()->windowToContents(platformMouseEvent.position());
2892 constexpr OptionSet<HitTestRequest::Type> hitType { HitTestRequest::Type::ReadOnly, HitTestRequest::Type::Active, HitTestRequest::Type::DisallowUserAgentShadowContent, HitTestRequest::Type::AllowChildFrameContent };
2893 HitTestResult result = page->corePage()->mainFrame().eventHandler().hitTestResultAtPoint(point, hitType);
2894
2895 Frame* frame = &page->corePage()->mainFrame();
2896 if (result.innerNonSharedNode())
2897 frame = result.innerNonSharedNode()->document().frame();
2898
2899 bool handled = page->corePage()->userInputBridge().handleContextMenuEvent(platformMouseEvent, *frame);
2900#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
2901 if (handled)
2902 page->contextMenu().show();
2903#endif
2904 return handled;
2905}
2906
2907void WebPage::contextMenuForKeyEvent()
2908{
2909#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
2910 corePage()->contextMenuController().clearContextMenu();
2911#endif
2912
2913 Frame& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
2914 bool handled = frame.eventHandler().sendContextMenuEventForKey();
2915#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
2916 if (handled)
2917 contextMenu().show();
2918#else
2919 UNUSED_PARAM(handled);
2920#endif
2921}
2922#endif
2923
2924static bool handleMouseEvent(const WebMouseEvent& mouseEvent, WebPage* page)
2925{
2926 Frame& frame = page->corePage()->mainFrame();
2927 if (!frame.view())
2928 return false;
2929
2930 PlatformMouseEvent platformMouseEvent = platform(mouseEvent);
2931
2932 switch (platformMouseEvent.type()) {
2933 case PlatformEvent::MousePressed: {
2934#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
2935 if (isContextClick(platformMouseEvent))
2936 page->corePage()->contextMenuController().clearContextMenu();
2937#endif
2938
2939 bool handled = page->corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMousePressEvent(platformMouseEvent);
2940#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENU_EVENT)
2941 if (isContextClick(platformMouseEvent))
2942 handled = handleContextMenuEvent(platformMouseEvent, page);
2943#endif
2944 return handled;
2945 }
2946 case PlatformEvent::MouseReleased:
2947 if (mouseEvent.gestureWasCancelled() == GestureWasCancelled::Yes)
2948 frame.eventHandler().invalidateClick();
2949 return page->corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMouseReleaseEvent(platformMouseEvent);
2950
2951 case PlatformEvent::MouseMoved:
2952#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
2953 // We need to do a full, normal hit test during this mouse event if the page is active or if a mouse
2954 // button is currently pressed. It is possible that neither of those things will be true since on
2955 // Lion when legacy scrollbars are enabled, WebKit receives mouse events all the time. If it is one
2956 // of those cases where the page is not active and the mouse is not pressed, then we can fire a more
2957 // efficient scrollbars-only version of the event.
2958 if (!(page->corePage()->focusController().isActive() || (mouseEvent.button() != WebMouseEvent::NoButton)))
2959 return page->corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMouseMoveOnScrollbarEvent(platformMouseEvent);
2960#endif
2961 return page->corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMouseMoveEvent(platformMouseEvent);
2962
2963 case PlatformEvent::MouseForceChanged:
2964 case PlatformEvent::MouseForceDown:
2965 case PlatformEvent::MouseForceUp:
2966 return page->corePage()->userInputBridge().handleMouseForceEvent(platformMouseEvent);
2967
2968 default:
2969 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2970 return false;
2971 }
2972}
2973
2974void WebPage::mouseEvent(const WebMouseEvent& mouseEvent, std::optional<SandboxExtension::HandleArray>&& sandboxExtensions)
2975{
2976 SetForScope<bool> userIsInteractingChange { m_userIsInteracting, true };
2977
2978 m_userActivity.impulse();
2979
2980 bool shouldHandleEvent = true;
2981
2982#if ENABLE(CONTEXT_MENUS)
2983 // Don't try to handle any pending mouse events if a context menu is showing.
2984 if (m_isShowingContextMenu)
2985 shouldHandleEvent = false;
2986#endif
2987#if ENABLE(DRAG_SUPPORT)
2988 if (m_isStartingDrag)
2989 shouldHandleEvent = false;
2990#endif
2991
2992 if (!shouldHandleEvent) {
2993 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveEvent(static_cast<uint32_t>(mouseEvent.type()), false));
2994 return;
2995 }
2996
2997 Vector<RefPtr<SandboxExtension>> mouseEventSandboxExtensions;
2998 if (sandboxExtensions)
2999 mouseEventSandboxExtensions = consumeSandboxExtensions(WTFMove(*sandboxExtensions));
3000
3001 bool handled = false;
3002
3003#if !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
3004 if (!handled && m_headerBanner)
3005 handled = m_headerBanner->mouseEvent(mouseEvent);
3006 if (!handled && m_footerBanner)
3007 handled = m_footerBanner->mouseEvent(mouseEvent);
3008#endif // !PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
3009
3010 if (!handled) {
3011 CurrentEvent currentEvent(mouseEvent);
3012 handled = handleMouseEvent(mouseEvent, this);
3013 }
3014
3015 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveEvent(static_cast<uint32_t>(mouseEvent.type()), handled));
3016
3017 revokeSandboxExtensions(mouseEventSandboxExtensions);
3018}

3020static bool handleWheelEvent(const WebWheelEvent& wheelEvent, Page* page, OptionSet<WheelEventProcessingSteps> processingSteps)
3021{
3022 Frame& frame = page->mainFrame();

3024 return false;

3029
3030bool WebPage::wheelEvent(const WebWheelEvent& wheelEvent, OptionSet<WheelEventProcessingSteps> processingSteps)
3031{
3032 m_userActivity.impulse();
3033
3034 CurrentEvent currentEvent(wheelEvent);
3035
3036 bool handled = handleWheelEvent(wheelEvent, m_page.get(), processingSteps);
3037
3038 if (processingSteps.contains(WheelEventProcessingSteps::MainThreadForScrolling))
3039 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveEvent(static_cast<uint32_t>(wheelEvent.type()), handled));
3040
3041 return handled;
3042}
3043
3044void WebPage::dispatchWheelEventWithoutScrolling(const WebWheelEvent& wheelEvent, CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
3045{
3046#if ENABLE(KINETIC_SCROLLING)
3047 auto gestureState = m_page->mainFrame().eventHandler().wheelScrollGestureState();
3048 bool isCancelable = !gestureState || gestureState == WheelScrollGestureState::Blocking || wheelEvent.phase() == WebWheelEvent::PhaseBegan;
3049#else
3050 bool isCancelable = true;
3051#endif
3052 bool handled = this->wheelEvent(wheelEvent, { isCancelable ? WheelEventProcessingSteps::MainThreadForBlockingDOMEventDispatch : WheelEventProcessingSteps::MainThreadForNonBlockingDOMEventDispatch });
3053 completionHandler(handled);
3054}

3056static bool handleKeyEvent(const WebKeyboardEvent& keyboardEvent, Page* page)
3057{
3058 if (!page->mainFrame().view())
3059 return false;
3060
3061 if (keyboardEvent.type() == WebEvent::Char && keyboardEvent.isSystemKey())
3062 return page->userInputBridge().handleAccessKeyEvent(platform(keyboardEvent));
3063 return page->userInputBridge().handleKeyEvent(platform(keyboardEvent));
3064}
3065
3066void WebPage::keyEvent(const WebKeyboardEvent& keyboardEvent)
3067{
3068 SetForScope<bool> userIsInteractingChange { m_userIsInteracting, true };
3069
3070 m_userActivity.impulse();
3071
3072 PlatformKeyboardEvent::setCurrentModifierState(platform(keyboardEvent).modifiers());
3073
3074 CurrentEvent currentEvent(keyboardEvent);
3075
3076 bool handled = handleKeyEvent(keyboardEvent, m_page.get());
3077 // FIXME: Platform default behaviors should be performed during normal DOM event dispatch (in most cases, in default keydown event handler).
3078 if (!handled)
3079 handled = performDefaultBehaviorForKeyEvent(keyboardEvent);
3080
3081 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveEvent(static_cast<uint32_t>(keyboardEvent.type()), handled));
3082}
3083
3084bool WebPage::handleKeyEventByRelinquishingFocusToChrome(const KeyboardEvent& event)
3085{
3086 if (m_page->tabKeyCyclesThroughElements())
3087 return false;
3088
3089 if (event.charCode() != '\t')
3090 return false;
3091
3092 if (!event.shiftKey() || event.ctrlKey() || event.metaKey() || event.altGraphKey())
3093 return false;
3094
3095 ASSERT(event.type() == eventNames().keypressEvent);
3096 // Allow a shift-tab keypress event to relinquish focus even if we don't allow tab to cycle between
3097 // elements inside the view. We can only do this for shift-tab, not tab itself because
3098 // tabKeyCyclesThroughElements is used to make tab character insertion work in editable web views.
3099 return m_page->focusController().relinquishFocusToChrome(FocusDirection::Backward);
3100}

3102void WebPage::validateCommand(const String& commandName, CompletionHandler<void(bool, int32_t)>&& completionHandler)
3103{
3104 bool isEnabled = false;
3105 int32_t state = 0;
3106 Frame& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
3107 if (PluginView* pluginView = focusedPluginViewForFrame(frame))
3108 isEnabled = pluginView->isEditingCommandEnabled(commandName);
3109 else {
3110 Editor::Command command = frame.editor().command(commandName);
3111 state = (command.state() != TriState::False);
3112 isEnabled = command.isSupported() && command.isEnabled();
3113 }
3114
3115 completionHandler(isEnabled, state);
3116}

3119{
3120 executeEditingCommand(commandName, argument);
3121}

3133
3134void WebPage::restoreSessionInternal(const Vector<BackForwardListItemState>& itemStates, WasRestoredByAPIRequest restoredByAPIRequest, WebBackForwardListProxy::OverwriteExistingItem overwrite)
3135{
3136 // Since we're merely restoring HistoryItems from the UIProcess, there is no need to send HistoryItem update notifications back to the UIProcess.
3137 // Also, with process-swap on navigation, these updates may actually overwrite important state in the UIProcess such as the scroll position.
3138 SetForScope<void (*)(WebCore::HistoryItem&)> bypassHistoryItemUpdateNotifications(WebCore::notifyHistoryItemChanged, [](WebCore::HistoryItem&){});
3139 for (const auto& itemState : itemStates) {
3140 auto historyItem = toHistoryItem(itemState);
3141 historyItem->setWasRestoredFromSession(restoredByAPIRequest == WasRestoredByAPIRequest::Yes);
3142 static_cast<WebBackForwardListProxy&>(corePage()->backForward().client()).addItemFromUIProcess(itemState.identifier, WTFMove(historyItem), m_identifier, overwrite);
3143 }
3144}
3145
3146void WebPage::restoreSession(const Vector<BackForwardListItemState>& itemStates)
3147{
3148 restoreSessionInternal(itemStates, WasRestoredByAPIRequest::Yes, WebBackForwardListProxy::OverwriteExistingItem::No);
3149}
3150
3151void WebPage::updateBackForwardListForReattach(const Vector<WebKit::BackForwardListItemState>& itemStates)
3152{
3153 restoreSessionInternal(itemStates, WasRestoredByAPIRequest::No, WebBackForwardListProxy::OverwriteExistingItem::Yes);
3154}

3182#if ENABLE(TOUCH_EVENTS)
3183static bool handleTouchEvent(const WebTouchEvent& touchEvent, Page* page)
3184{
3185 if (!page->mainFrame().view())
3186 return false;
3187

3189}
3190#endif
3191
3192#if ENABLE(IOS_TOUCH_EVENTS)
3193bool WebPage::dispatchTouchEvent(const WebTouchEvent& touchEvent)
3194{
3195 SetForScope<bool> userIsInteractingChange { m_userIsInteracting, true };
3196 m_lastInteractionLocation = touchEvent.position();
3197 CurrentEvent currentEvent(touchEvent);
3198 bool handled = handleTouchEvent(touchEvent, m_page.get());
3199 updatePotentialTapSecurityOrigin(touchEvent, handled);
3200 return handled;
3201}
3202
3203void WebPage::touchEventSync(const WebTouchEvent& touchEvent, CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& reply)
3204{
3205 // Avoid UIProcess hangs when the WebContent process is stuck on a sync IPC.
3206 if (IPC::UnboundedSynchronousIPCScope::hasOngoingUnboundedSyncIPC()) {
3207 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Process, "touchEventSync: Not processing because the process is stuck on unbounded sync IPC");
3208 return reply(true);
3209 }
3210
3211 m_pendingSynchronousTouchEventReply = WTFMove(reply);
3212
3213 EventDispatcher::TouchEventQueue queuedEvents;
3214 WebProcess::singleton().eventDispatcher().takeQueuedTouchEventsForPage(*this, queuedEvents);
3215 dispatchAsynchronousTouchEvents(WTFMove(queuedEvents));
3216
3217 bool handled = dispatchTouchEvent(touchEvent);
3218
3219 if (auto reply = WTFMove(m_pendingSynchronousTouchEventReply))
3220 reply(handled);
3221}
3222
3223void WebPage::resetPotentialTapSecurityOrigin()
3224{
3225 m_potentialTapSecurityOrigin = nullptr;
3226}
3227
3228void WebPage::updatePotentialTapSecurityOrigin(const WebTouchEvent& touchEvent, bool wasHandled)
3229{
3230 if (wasHandled)
3231 return;
3232
3233 if (!touchEvent.isPotentialTap())
3234 return;
3235
3236 if (touchEvent.type() != WebEvent::TouchStart)
3237 return;
3238
3239 auto& mainFrame = m_page->mainFrame();
3240 auto document = mainFrame.document();
3241 if (!document)
3242 return;
3243
3244 if (!document->handlingTouchEvent())
3245 return;
3246
3247 Frame* touchEventTargetFrame = &mainFrame;
3248 while (auto subframe = touchEventTargetFrame->eventHandler().touchEventTargetSubframe())
3249 touchEventTargetFrame = subframe;
3250
3251 auto& touches = touchEventTargetFrame->eventHandler().touches();
3252 if (touches.isEmpty())
3253 return;
3254
3255 ASSERT(touches.size() == 1);
3256
3257 if (auto targetDocument = touchEventTargetFrame->document())
3258 m_potentialTapSecurityOrigin = &targetDocument->securityOrigin();
3259}
3260#elif ENABLE(TOUCH_EVENTS)
3261void WebPage::touchEvent(const WebTouchEvent& touchEvent)
3262{
3263 CurrentEvent currentEvent(touchEvent);
3264
3265 bool handled = handleTouchEvent(touchEvent, m_page.get());
3266
3267 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveEvent(static_cast<uint32_t>(touchEvent.type()), handled));
3268}
3269#endif

3414void WebPage::setInitialFocus(bool forward, bool isKeyboardEventValid, const WebKeyboardEvent& event, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
3415{
3416 if (!m_page)
3417 return completionHandler();
3418
3419 SetForScope<bool> userIsInteractingChange { m_userIsInteracting, true };
3420
3421 Frame& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
3422 frame.document()->setFocusedElement(0);
3423
3424 if (isKeyboardEventValid && event.type() == WebEvent::KeyDown) {
3425 PlatformKeyboardEvent platformEvent(platform(event));
3426 platformEvent.disambiguateKeyDownEvent(PlatformEvent::RawKeyDown);
3427 m_page->focusController().setInitialFocus(forward ? FocusDirection::Forward : FocusDirection::Backward, &KeyboardEvent::create(platformEvent, &frame.windowProxy()).get());
3428 completionHandler();
3429 return;
3430 }
3431
3432 m_page->focusController().setInitialFocus(forward ? FocusDirection::Forward : FocusDirection::Backward, nullptr);
3433 completionHandler();
3434}

3439 m_page->setCanStartMedia(true);

3441
3442void WebPage::updateIsInWindow(bool isInitialState)
3443{
3444 bool isInWindow = m_activityState.contains(WebCore::ActivityState::IsInWindow);
3445
3446 if (!isInWindow) {
3447 m_setCanStartMediaTimer.stop();
3448 m_page->setCanStartMedia(false);
3449
3450 // The WebProcess does not yet know about this page; no need to tell it we're leaving the window.
3451 if (!isInitialState)
3452 WebProcess::singleton().pageWillLeaveWindow(m_identifier);
3453 } else {
3454 // Defer the call to Page::setCanStartMedia() since it ends up sending a synchronous message to the UI process
3455 // in order to get plug-in connections, and the UI process will be waiting for the Web process to update the backing
3456 // store after moving the view into a window, until it times out and paints white. See <rdar://problem/9242771>.
3457 if (m_mayStartMediaWhenInWindow)
3458 m_setCanStartMediaTimer.startOneShot(0_s);
3459
3460 WebProcess::singleton().pageDidEnterWindow(m_identifier);
3461 }
3462
3463 if (isInWindow)
3464 layoutIfNeeded();
3465}
3466
3467void WebPage::visibilityDidChange()
3468{
3469 bool isVisible = m_activityState.contains(ActivityState::IsVisible);
3470 if (!isVisible) {
3471 // We save the document / scroll state when backgrounding a tab so that we are able to restore it
3472 // if it gets terminated while in the background.
3473 if (auto* frame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame())
3474 frame->loader().history().saveDocumentAndScrollState();
3475 }
3476}
3477
3478void WebPage::setActivityState(OptionSet<ActivityState::Flag> activityState, ActivityStateChangeID activityStateChangeID, CompletionHandler<void()>&& callback)
3479{
3480 LOG_WITH_STREAM(ActivityState, stream << "WebPage " << identifier().toUInt64() << " setActivityState to " << activityState);
3481
3482 auto changed = m_activityState ^ activityState;
3483 m_activityState = activityState;
3484
3485 if (changed)
3486 updateThrottleState();
3487
3488 ASSERT_WITH_MESSAGE(m_page, "setActivityState called on %" PRIu64 " but WebCore page was null", identifier().toUInt64());
3489 if (m_page) {
3490 SetForScope<OptionSet<ActivityState::Flag>> currentlyChangingActivityState { m_lastActivityStateChanges, changed };
3491 m_page->setActivityState(activityState);
3492 }
3493
3494 for (auto* pluginView : m_pluginViews)
3495 pluginView->activityStateDidChange(changed);
3496
3497 m_drawingArea->activityStateDidChange(changed, activityStateChangeID, WTFMove(callback));
3498 WebProcess::singleton().pageActivityStateDidChange(m_identifier, changed);
3499
3500 if (changed & ActivityState::IsInWindow)
3501 updateIsInWindow();
3502
3503 if (changed & ActivityState::IsVisible)
3504 visibilityDidChange();
3505}

3540void WebPage::didStartPageTransition()
3541{
3542 freezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::PageTransition);
3543
3544#if PLATFORM(MAC)
3545 bool hasPreviouslyFocusedDueToUserInteraction = m_hasEverFocusedElementDueToUserInteractionSincePageTransition;
3546#endif
3547 m_hasEverFocusedElementDueToUserInteractionSincePageTransition = false;
3548 m_lastEditorStateWasContentEditable = EditorStateIsContentEditable::Unset;
3549
3550#if PLATFORM(MAC)
3551 if (hasPreviouslyFocusedDueToUserInteraction)
3552 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetHasHadSelectionChangesFromUserInteraction(m_hasEverFocusedElementDueToUserInteractionSincePageTransition));
3553#endif
3554
3555#if HAVE(TOUCH_BAR)
3556 if (m_isTouchBarUpdateSupressedForHiddenContentEditable) {
3557 m_isTouchBarUpdateSupressedForHiddenContentEditable = false;
3558 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetIsTouchBarUpdateSupressedForHiddenContentEditable(m_isTouchBarUpdateSupressedForHiddenContentEditable));
3559 }
3560
3561 if (m_isNeverRichlyEditableForTouchBar) {
3562 m_isNeverRichlyEditableForTouchBar = false;
3563 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetIsNeverRichlyEditableForTouchBar(m_isNeverRichlyEditableForTouchBar));
3564 }
3565#endif
3566
3567#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
3568 m_isShowingInputViewForFocusedElement = false;
3569 // This is used to enable a first-tap quirk.
3570 m_hasHandledSyntheticClick = false;
3571#endif
3572}

3630void WebPage::suspend(CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
3631{
3632 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Loading, "suspend: m_page=%p", m_page.get());
3633 if (!m_page)
3634 return completionHandler(false);
3635
3636 freezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::PageSuspended);
3637
3638 m_cachedPage = BackForwardCache::singleton().suspendPage(*m_page);
3639 ASSERT(m_cachedPage);
3640 if (auto mainFrame = m_mainFrame->coreFrame())
3641 mainFrame->loader().detachFromAllOpenedFrames();
3642 completionHandler(true);
3643}
3644
3645void WebPage::resume(CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
3646{
3647 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Loading, "resume: m_page=%p", m_page.get());
3648 if (!m_page)
3649 return completionHandler(false);
3650
3651 auto cachedPage = std::exchange(m_cachedPage, nullptr);
3652 ASSERT(cachedPage);
3653 if (!cachedPage)
3654 return completionHandler(false);
3655
3656 cachedPage->restore(*m_page);
3657 unfreezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::PageSuspended);
3658 completionHandler(true);
3659}

3694
3695void WebPage::runJavaScript(WebFrame* frame, RunJavaScriptParameters&& parameters, ContentWorldIdentifier worldIdentifier, CompletionHandler<void(const IPC::DataReference&, const std::optional<WebCore::ExceptionDetails>&)>&& completionHandler)
3696{
3697 // NOTE: We need to be careful when running scripts that the objects we depend on don't
3698 // disappear during script execution.
3699
3700 if (!frame || !frame->coreFrame()) {
3701 completionHandler({ }, ExceptionDetails { "Unable to execute JavaScript: Target frame could not be found in the page"_s, 0, 0, ExceptionDetails::Type::InvalidTargetFrame });
3702 return;
3703 }
3704
3705 auto* world = m_userContentController->worldForIdentifier(worldIdentifier);
3706 if (!world) {
3707 completionHandler({ }, ExceptionDetails { "Unable to execute JavaScript: Cannot find specified content world"_s });
3708 return;
3709 }
3710
3711#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
3712 if (frame->shouldEnableInAppBrowserPrivacyProtections()) {
3713 completionHandler({ }, ExceptionDetails { "Unable to execute JavaScript in a frame that is not in an app-bound domain"_s, 0, 0, ExceptionDetails::Type::AppBoundDomain });
3714 if (auto* document = m_page->mainFrame().document())
3715 document->addConsoleMessage(MessageSource::Security, MessageLevel::Warning, "Ignoring user script injection for non-app bound domain.");
3716 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Loading, "runJavaScript: Ignoring user script injection for non app-bound domain");
3717 return;
3718 }
3719#endif
3720
3721 auto resolveFunction = [world = makeRef(*world), frame = makeRef(*frame), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (ValueOrException result) mutable {
3722 RefPtr<SerializedScriptValue> serializedResultValue;
3723 if (result) {
3724 serializedResultValue = SerializedScriptValue::create(frame->jsContextForWorld(world.ptr()),
3725 toRef(frame->coreFrame()->script().globalObject(world->coreWorld()), result.value()), nullptr);
3726 }
3727
3728 IPC::DataReference dataReference;
3729 if (serializedResultValue)
3730 dataReference = serializedResultValue->data();
3731
3732 std::optional<ExceptionDetails> details;
3733 if (!result)
3734 details = result.error();
3735
3736 completionHandler(dataReference, details);
3737 };
3738 JSLockHolder lock(commonVM());
3739 frame->coreFrame()->script().executeAsynchronousUserAgentScriptInWorld(world->coreWorld(), WTFMove(parameters), WTFMove(resolveFunction));
3740}
3741
3742void WebPage::runJavaScriptInFrameInScriptWorld(RunJavaScriptParameters&& parameters, std::optional<WebCore::FrameIdentifier> frameID, const std::pair<ContentWorldIdentifier, String>& worldData, CompletionHandler<void(const IPC::DataReference&, const std::optional<WebCore::ExceptionDetails>&)>&& completionHandler)
3743{
3744 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Process, "runJavaScriptInFrameInScriptWorld: frameID=%" PRIu64, frameID.value_or(WebCore::FrameIdentifier { }).toUInt64());
3745 auto webFrame = makeRefPtr(frameID ? WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(*frameID) : &mainWebFrame());
3746
3747 if (auto* newWorld = m_userContentController->addContentWorld(worldData)) {
3748 auto& coreWorld = newWorld->coreWorld();
3749 for (RefPtr<Frame> frame = mainFrame(); frame; frame = frame->tree().traverseNext())
3750 frame->loader().client().dispatchGlobalObjectAvailable(coreWorld);
3751 }
3752
3753 runJavaScript(webFrame.get(), WTFMove(parameters), worldData.first, [this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](const IPC::DataReference& result, const std::optional<WebCore::ExceptionDetails>& exception) mutable {
3754 if (exception)
3755 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Process, "runJavaScriptInFrameInScriptWorld: Request to run JavaScript failed with error %{private}s", exception->message.utf8().data());
3756 else
3757 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Process, "runJavaScriptInFrameInScriptWorld: Request to run JavaScript succeeded");
3758 completionHandler(result, exception);
3759 });
3760}
3761
3762void WebPage::getContentsAsString(ContentAsStringIncludesChildFrames includeChildFrames, CompletionHandler<void(const String&)>&& callback)
3763{
3764 switch (includeChildFrames) {
3765 case ContentAsStringIncludesChildFrames::No:
3766 callback(m_mainFrame->contentsAsString());
3767 break;
3768 case ContentAsStringIncludesChildFrames::Yes:
3769 StringBuilder builder;
3770 for (auto frame = makeRefPtr(m_mainFrame->coreFrame()); frame; frame = frame->tree().traverseNextRendered()) {
3771 if (auto webFrame = WebFrame::fromCoreFrame(*frame))
3772 builder.append(builder.isEmpty() ? "" : "\n\n", webFrame->contentsAsString());
3773 }
3774 callback(builder.toString());
3775 break;
3776 }
3777}
3778
3779#if ENABLE(MHTML)

3790
3791static Frame* frameWithSelection(Page* page)
3792{
3793 for (Frame* frame = &page->mainFrame(); frame; frame = frame->tree().traverseNext()) {
3794 if (frame->selection().isRange())
3795 return frame;
3796 }
3797 return nullptr;
3798}
3799
3800void WebPage::getSelectionAsWebArchiveData(CompletionHandler<void(const std::optional<IPC::DataReference>&)>&& callback)
3801{
3802#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
3803 RetainPtr<CFDataRef> data;
3804 if (Frame* frame = frameWithSelection(m_page.get()))
3805 data = LegacyWebArchive::createFromSelection(frame)->rawDataRepresentation();
3806#endif
3807
3808 IPC::DataReference dataReference;
3809#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
3810 if (data)
3811 dataReference = { CFDataGetBytePtr(data.get()), static_cast<size_t>(CFDataGetLength(data.get())) };
3812#endif
3813 callback(dataReference);
3814}

3816void WebPage::getSelectionOrContentsAsString(CompletionHandler<void(const String&)>&& callback)
3817{
3818 WebFrame* focusedOrMainFrame = WebFrame::fromCoreFrame(m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame());
3819 String resultString = focusedOrMainFrame->selectionAsString();
3820 if (resultString.isEmpty())
3821 resultString = focusedOrMainFrame->contentsAsString();
3822 callback(resultString);
3823}

3825void WebPage::getSourceForFrame(FrameIdentifier frameID, CompletionHandler<void(const String&)>&& callback)
3826{
3827 String resultString;
3828 if (WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID))
3829 resultString = frame->source();
3830
3831 callback(resultString);
3832}
3833
3834void WebPage::getMainResourceDataOfFrame(FrameIdentifier frameID, CompletionHandler<void(const std::optional<IPC::SharedBufferDataReference>&)>&& callback)
3835{
3836 RefPtr<SharedBuffer> buffer;
3837 if (WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID)) {
3838 if (PluginView* pluginView = pluginViewForFrame(frame->coreFrame()))
3839 buffer = pluginView->liveResourceData();
3840 if (!buffer) {
3841 if (DocumentLoader* loader = frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader())
3842 buffer = loader->mainResourceData();
3843 }
3844 }
3845
3846 IPC::SharedBufferDataReference dataReference;
3847 if (buffer)
3848 dataReference = { *buffer };
3849 callback(dataReference);
3850}
3851
3852static RefPtr<SharedBuffer> resourceDataForFrame(Frame* frame, const URL& resourceURL)
3853{
3854 DocumentLoader* loader = frame->loader().documentLoader();
3855 if (!loader)
3856 return nullptr;
3857
3858 RefPtr<ArchiveResource> subresource = loader->subresource(resourceURL);
3859 if (!subresource)
3860 return nullptr;
3861
3862 return &subresource->data();
3863}
3864
3865void WebPage::getResourceDataFromFrame(FrameIdentifier frameID, const String& resourceURLString, CompletionHandler<void(const std::optional<IPC::SharedBufferDataReference>&)>&& callback)
3866{
3867 RefPtr<SharedBuffer> buffer;
3868 if (auto* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID)) {
3869 URL resourceURL(URL(), resourceURLString);
3870 buffer = resourceDataForFrame(frame->coreFrame(), resourceURL);
3871 }
3872
3873 IPC::SharedBufferDataReference dataReference;
3874 if (buffer)
3875 dataReference = { *buffer };
3876 callback(dataReference);
3877}
3878
3879void WebPage::getWebArchiveOfFrame(FrameIdentifier frameID, CompletionHandler<void(const std::optional<IPC::DataReference>&)>&& callback)
3880{
3881#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
3882 RetainPtr<CFDataRef> data;
3883 if (WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID))
3884 data = frame->webArchiveData(nullptr, nullptr);
3885#else
3886 UNUSED_PARAM(frameID);
3887#endif
3888
3889 IPC::DataReference dataReference;
3890#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
3891 if (data)
3892 dataReference = { CFDataGetBytePtr(data.get()), static_cast<size_t>(CFDataGetLength(data.get())) };
3893#endif
3894 callback(dataReference);
3895}

3921void WebPage::updatePreferences(const WebPreferencesStore& store)
3922{
3923 updatePreferencesGenerated(store);
3924 updateSettingsGenerated(store);
3925
3926 Settings& settings = m_page->settings();
3927
3928#if !PLATFORM(GTK) && !PLATFORM(WIN) && !PLATFORM(PLAYSTATION)
3929 if (!settings.acceleratedCompositingEnabled()) {
3930 WEBPAGE_RELEASE_LOG(Layers, "updatePreferences: acceleratedCompositingEnabled setting was false. WebKit cannot function in this mode; changing setting to true");
3931 settings.setAcceleratedCompositingEnabled(true);
3932 }
3933#endif
3934
3935 bool requiresUserGestureForMedia = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::requiresUserGestureForMediaPlaybackKey());
3936 settings.setVideoPlaybackRequiresUserGesture(requiresUserGestureForMedia || store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::requiresUserGestureForVideoPlaybackKey()));
3937 settings.setAudioPlaybackRequiresUserGesture(requiresUserGestureForMedia || store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::requiresUserGestureForAudioPlaybackKey()));
3938 settings.setUserInterfaceDirectionPolicy(static_cast<WebCore::UserInterfaceDirectionPolicy>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::userInterfaceDirectionPolicyKey())));
3939 settings.setSystemLayoutDirection(static_cast<TextDirection>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::systemLayoutDirectionKey())));
3940 settings.setJavaScriptRuntimeFlags(static_cast<RuntimeFlags>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::javaScriptRuntimeFlagsKey())));
3941 settings.setStorageBlockingPolicy(static_cast<StorageBlockingPolicy>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::storageBlockingPolicyKey())));
3942 settings.setFrameFlattening(store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::frameFlatteningEnabledKey()) ? WebCore::FrameFlattening::FullyEnabled : WebCore::FrameFlattening::Disabled);
3943 settings.setEditableLinkBehavior(static_cast<WebCore::EditableLinkBehavior>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::editableLinkBehaviorKey())));
3944#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)
3945 settings.setDataDetectorTypes(static_cast<DataDetectorType>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::dataDetectorTypesKey())));
3946#endif
3947 settings.setPitchCorrectionAlgorithm(static_cast<MediaPlayerEnums::PitchCorrectionAlgorithm>(store.getUInt32ValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::pitchCorrectionAlgorithmKey())));
3948
3949 DatabaseManager::singleton().setIsAvailable(store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::databasesEnabledKey()));
3950
3951 m_tabToLinks = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::tabsToLinksKey());
3952 m_asynchronousPluginInitializationEnabled = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::asynchronousPluginInitializationEnabledKey());
3953 m_asynchronousPluginInitializationEnabledForAllPlugins = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::asynchronousPluginInitializationEnabledForAllPluginsKey());
3954 m_artificialPluginInitializationDelayEnabled = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::artificialPluginInitializationDelayEnabledKey());
3955
3956 bool isAppNapEnabled = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::pageVisibilityBasedProcessSuppressionEnabledKey());
3957 if (m_isAppNapEnabled != isAppNapEnabled) {
3958 m_isAppNapEnabled = isAppNapEnabled;
3959 updateThrottleState();
3960 }
3961
3962#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
3963 m_pdfPluginEnabled = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::pdfPluginEnabledKey());
3964#endif
3965#if ENABLE(PAYMENT_REQUEST)
3966 settings.setPaymentRequestEnabled(store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::applePayEnabledKey()));
3967#endif
3968
3969#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
3970 setForceAlwaysUserScalable(m_forceAlwaysUserScalable || store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::forceAlwaysUserScalableKey()));
3971#endif
3972
3973#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
3974 if (store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::serviceWorkerEntitlementDisabledForTestingKey()))
3975 disableServiceWorkerEntitlement();
3976#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
3977 bool shouldAllowServiceWorkersForAppBoundViews = m_limitsNavigationsToAppBoundDomains;
3978#else
3979 bool shouldAllowServiceWorkersForAppBoundViews = false;
3980#endif
3981
3982 if (store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::serviceWorkersEnabledKey())) {
3983 ASSERT(parentProcessHasServiceWorkerEntitlement() || shouldAllowServiceWorkersForAppBoundViews);
3984 if (!parentProcessHasServiceWorkerEntitlement() && !shouldAllowServiceWorkersForAppBoundViews)
3985 RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().setServiceWorkerEnabled(false);
3986 }
3987#endif
3988
3989#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
3990 m_needsInAppBrowserPrivacyQuirks = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::needsInAppBrowserPrivacyQuirksKey());
3991#endif
3992
3993 settings.setPrivateClickMeasurementEnabled(store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::privateClickMeasurementEnabledKey()));
3994
3995 if (m_drawingArea)
3996 m_drawingArea->updatePreferences(store);
3997
3998#if USE(LIBWEBRTC)
3999 m_page->libWebRTCProvider().setH265Support(RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().webRTCH265CodecEnabled());
4000 m_page->libWebRTCProvider().setVP9Support(RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().webRTCVP9Profile0CodecEnabled(), RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().webRTCVP9Profile2CodecEnabled());
4001 LibWebRTCProvider::setH264HardwareEncoderAllowed(store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::webRTCH264HardwareEncoderEnabledKey()));
4002#endif
4003
4004#if ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
4005 // FIXME: useGPUProcessForMediaEnabled should be a RuntimeEnabledFeature since it's global.
4006 static_cast<WebMediaStrategy&>(platformStrategies()->mediaStrategy()).setUseGPUProcess(m_shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess);
4007 WebProcess::singleton().supplement<RemoteMediaPlayerManager>()->setUseGPUProcess(m_shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess);
4008#if HAVE(AVASSETREADER)
4009 WebProcess::singleton().supplement<RemoteImageDecoderAVFManager>()->setUseGPUProcess(m_shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess);
4010#endif
4011 WebProcess::singleton().setUseGPUProcessForCanvasRendering(m_shouldRenderCanvasInGPUProcess);
4012 bool usingGPUProcessForDOMRendering = m_shouldRenderDOMInGPUProcess && DrawingArea::supportsGPUProcessRendering(m_drawingAreaType);
4013 WebProcess::singleton().setUseGPUProcessForDOMRendering(usingGPUProcessForDOMRendering);
4014 WebProcess::singleton().setUseGPUProcessForMedia(m_shouldPlayMediaInGPUProcess);
4015#if ENABLE(WEBGL)
4016 WebProcess::singleton().setUseGPUProcessForWebGL(m_shouldRenderWebGLInGPUProcess);
4017#endif
4018#endif // ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
4019
4020#if ENABLE(IPC_TESTING_API)
4021 m_ipcTestingAPIEnabled = store.getBoolValueForKey(WebPreferencesKey::ipcTestingAPIEnabledKey());
4022
4023 WebProcess::singleton().parentProcessConnection()->setIgnoreInvalidMessageForTesting();
4024 if (auto* gpuProcessConnection = WebProcess::singleton().existingGPUProcessConnection())
4025 gpuProcessConnection->connection().setIgnoreInvalidMessageForTesting();
4026#endif
4027
4028#if ENABLE(WEB_AUTHN) && PLATFORM(IOS)
4029 if (isParentProcessAWebBrowser())
4030 settings.setWebAuthenticationEnabled(true);
4031#endif
4032
4033#if ENABLE(WEBM_FORMAT_READER)
4034 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setWebMFormatReaderEnabled(RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().webMFormatReaderEnabled());
4035#endif
4036
4037#if ENABLE(VORBIS) && PLATFORM(MAC)
4038 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setVorbisDecoderEnabled(RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().vorbisDecoderEnabled());
4039#endif
4040
4041#if ENABLE(OPUS) && PLATFORM(MAC)
4042 PlatformMediaSessionManager::setOpusDecoderEnabled(RuntimeEnabledFeatures::sharedFeatures().opusDecoderEnabled());
4043#endif

4048void WebPage::setDataDetectionResults(NSArray *detectionResults)

4054
4055void WebPage::removeDataDetectedLinks(CompletionHandler<void(const DataDetectionResult&)>&& completionHandler)
4056{
4057 for (auto frame = makeRefPtr(&m_page->mainFrame()); frame; frame = frame->tree().traverseNext()) {
4058 auto document = makeRefPtr(frame->document());
4059 if (!document)
4060 continue;
4061
4062 DataDetection::removeDataDetectedLinksInDocument(*document);
4063
4064 if (auto* results = frame->dataDetectionResultsIfExists()) {
4065 // FIXME: It seems odd that we're clearing out all data detection results here,
4066 // instead of only data detectors that correspond to links.
4067 results->setDocumentLevelResults({ });
4068 }
4069 }
4070 completionHandler({ });
4071}
4072
4073void WebPage::detectDataInAllFrames(uint64_t types, CompletionHandler<void(const DataDetectionResult&)>&& completionHandler)
4074{
4075 DataDetectionResult mainFrameResult;
4076 auto dataDetectorTypes = OptionSet<DataDetectorType>::fromRaw(types);
4077 for (auto frame = makeRefPtr(&m_page->mainFrame()); frame; frame = frame->tree().traverseNext()) {
4078 auto document = makeRefPtr(frame->document());
4079 if (!document)
4080 continue;
4081 auto results = retainPtr(DataDetection::detectContentInRange(makeRangeSelectingNodeContents(*document), dataDetectorTypes, m_dataDetectionContext.get()));
4082 frame->dataDetectionResults().setDocumentLevelResults(results.get());
4083 if (frame->isMainFrame())
4084 mainFrameResult.results = WTFMove(results);
4085 }
4086 completionHandler(WTFMove(mainFrameResult));
4087}
4088
4089std::optional<std::pair<Ref<WebCore::HTMLElement>, WebCore::IntRect>> WebPage::findDataDetectionResultElementInImageOverlay(const FloatPoint& location, const HTMLElement& imageOverlayHost)
4090{
4091 Vector<Ref<HTMLElement>> dataDetectorElements;
4092 for (auto& child : descendantsOfType<HTMLElement>(*imageOverlayHost.shadowRoot())) {
4093 if (child.isImageOverlayDataDetectorResult())
4094 dataDetectorElements.append(child);
4095 }
4096
4097 for (auto& element : dataDetectorElements) {
4098 auto elementBounds = element->boundsInRootViewSpace();
4099 if (elementBounds.contains(roundedIntPoint(location)))
4100 return {{ WTFMove(element), elementBounds }};
4101 }
4102
4103 return std::nullopt;
4104}
4105
4106#endif // ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION)

4108#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
4109void WebPage::willCommitLayerTree(RemoteLayerTreeTransaction& layerTransaction)
4110{
4111 FrameView* frameView = corePage()->mainFrame().view();
4112 if (!frameView)
4113 return;
4114
4115 layerTransaction.setContentsSize(frameView->contentsSize());
4116 layerTransaction.setScrollOrigin(frameView->scrollOrigin());
4117 layerTransaction.setPageScaleFactor(corePage()->pageScaleFactor());
4118 layerTransaction.setRenderTreeSize(corePage()->renderTreeSize());
4119 layerTransaction.setThemeColor(corePage()->themeColor());
4120 layerTransaction.setPageExtendedBackgroundColor(corePage()->pageExtendedBackgroundColor());
4121 layerTransaction.setSampledPageTopColor(corePage()->sampledPageTopColor());
4122
4123 layerTransaction.setBaseLayoutViewportSize(frameView->baseLayoutViewportSize());
4124 layerTransaction.setMinStableLayoutViewportOrigin(frameView->minStableLayoutViewportOrigin());
4125 layerTransaction.setMaxStableLayoutViewportOrigin(frameView->maxStableLayoutViewportOrigin());
4126
4127#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
4128 layerTransaction.setScaleWasSetByUIProcess(scaleWasSetByUIProcess());
4129 layerTransaction.setMinimumScaleFactor(m_viewportConfiguration.minimumScale());
4130 layerTransaction.setMaximumScaleFactor(m_viewportConfiguration.maximumScale());
4131 layerTransaction.setInitialScaleFactor(m_viewportConfiguration.initialScale());
4132 layerTransaction.setViewportMetaTagWidth(m_viewportConfiguration.viewportArguments().width);
4133 layerTransaction.setViewportMetaTagWidthWasExplicit(m_viewportConfiguration.viewportArguments().widthWasExplicit);
4134 layerTransaction.setViewportMetaTagCameFromImageDocument(m_viewportConfiguration.viewportArguments().type == ViewportArguments::ImageDocument);
4135 layerTransaction.setAvoidsUnsafeArea(m_viewportConfiguration.avoidsUnsafeArea());
4136 layerTransaction.setIsInStableState(m_isInStableState);
4137 layerTransaction.setAllowsUserScaling(allowsUserScaling());
4138 if (m_pendingDynamicViewportSizeUpdateID) {
4139 layerTransaction.setDynamicViewportSizeUpdateID(*m_pendingDynamicViewportSizeUpdateID);
4140 m_pendingDynamicViewportSizeUpdateID = std::nullopt;
4141 }
4142 if (m_lastTransactionPageScaleFactor != layerTransaction.pageScaleFactor()) {
4143 m_lastTransactionPageScaleFactor = layerTransaction.pageScaleFactor();
4144 m_lastTransactionIDWithScaleChange = layerTransaction.transactionID();
4145 }
4146#endif
4147
4148 layerTransaction.setScrollPosition(frameView->scrollPosition());
4149
4150 m_pendingThemeColorChange = false;
4151 m_pendingPageExtendedBackgroundColorChange = false;
4152 m_pendingSampledPageTopColorChange = false;
4153
4154 if (m_hasPendingEditorStateUpdate) {
4155 layerTransaction.setEditorState(editorState());
4156 m_hasPendingEditorStateUpdate = false;
4157 }
4158}

4160void WebPage::didFlushLayerTreeAtTime(MonotonicTime timestamp)
4161{
4162#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
4163 if (m_oldestNonStableUpdateVisibleContentRectsTimestamp != MonotonicTime()) {
4164 Seconds elapsed = timestamp - m_oldestNonStableUpdateVisibleContentRectsTimestamp;
4165 m_oldestNonStableUpdateVisibleContentRectsTimestamp = MonotonicTime();
4166
4167 m_estimatedLatency = m_estimatedLatency * 0.80 + elapsed * 0.20;
4168 }
4169#else
4170 UNUSED_PARAM(timestamp);
4171#endif
4172}
4173#endif

4299void WebPage::enqueueSecurityPolicyViolationEvent(FrameIdentifier frameID, SecurityPolicyViolationEvent::Init&& eventInit)
4300{
4301 auto* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
4302 if (!frame)
4303 return;
4304 auto* coreFrame = frame->coreFrame();
4305 if (!coreFrame)
4306 return;
4307 if (auto* document = coreFrame->document())
4308 document->enqueueSecurityPolicyViolationEvent(WTFMove(eventInit));
4309}

4320#if ENABLE(DRAG_SUPPORT)
4321
4322#if PLATFORM(GTK)
4323void WebPage::performDragControllerAction(DragControllerAction action, const IntPoint& clientPosition, const IntPoint& globalPosition, OptionSet<DragOperation> draggingSourceOperationMask, SelectionData&& selectionData, OptionSet<DragApplicationFlags> flags)
4324{
4325 if (!m_page) {
4326 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(std::nullopt, DragHandlingMethod::None, false, 0, { }, { }));
4327 return;
4328 }
4329
4330 DragData dragData(&selectionData, clientPosition, globalPosition, draggingSourceOperationMask, flags, anyDragDestinationAction(), m_identifier);
4331 switch (action) {
4332 case DragControllerAction::Entered: {
4333 auto resolvedDragOperation = m_page->dragController().dragEntered(dragData);
4334 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(resolvedDragOperation, m_page->dragController().dragHandlingMethod(), m_page->dragController().mouseIsOverFileInput(), m_page->dragController().numberOfItemsToBeAccepted(), { }, { }));
4335 return;
4336 }
4337 case DragControllerAction::Updated: {
4338 auto resolvedDragOperation = m_page->dragController().dragUpdated(dragData);
4339 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(resolvedDragOperation, m_page->dragController().dragHandlingMethod(), m_page->dragController().mouseIsOverFileInput(), m_page->dragController().numberOfItemsToBeAccepted(), { }, { }));
4340 return;
4341 }
4342 case DragControllerAction::Exited:
4343 m_page->dragController().dragExited(dragData);
4344 return;
4345
4346 case DragControllerAction::PerformDragOperation: {
4347 m_page->dragController().performDragOperation(dragData);
4348 return;
4349 }
4350 }
4351 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4352}
4353#else
4354void WebPage::performDragControllerAction(DragControllerAction action, const WebCore::DragData& dragData, SandboxExtension::Handle&& sandboxExtensionHandle, SandboxExtension::HandleArray&& sandboxExtensionsHandleArray)
4355{
4356 if (!m_page) {
4357 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(std::nullopt, DragHandlingMethod::None, false, 0, { }, { }));
4358 return;
4359 }
4360
4361 switch (action) {
4362 case DragControllerAction::Entered: {
4363 auto resolvedDragOperation = m_page->dragController().dragEntered(dragData);
4364 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(resolvedDragOperation, m_page->dragController().dragHandlingMethod(), m_page->dragController().mouseIsOverFileInput(), m_page->dragController().numberOfItemsToBeAccepted(), m_page->dragCaretController().caretRectInRootViewCoordinates(), m_page->dragCaretController().editableElementRectInRootViewCoordinates()));
4365 return;
4366 }
4367 case DragControllerAction::Updated: {
4368 auto resolvedDragOperation = m_page->dragController().dragUpdated(dragData);
4369 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(resolvedDragOperation, m_page->dragController().dragHandlingMethod(), m_page->dragController().mouseIsOverFileInput(), m_page->dragController().numberOfItemsToBeAccepted(), m_page->dragCaretController().caretRectInRootViewCoordinates(), m_page->dragCaretController().editableElementRectInRootViewCoordinates()));
4370 return;
4371 }
4372 case DragControllerAction::Exited:
4373 m_page->dragController().dragExited(dragData);
4374 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragControllerAction(std::nullopt, DragHandlingMethod::None, false, 0, { }, { }));
4375 return;
4376
4377 case DragControllerAction::PerformDragOperation: {
4378 ASSERT(!m_pendingDropSandboxExtension);
4379
4380 m_pendingDropSandboxExtension = SandboxExtension::create(WTFMove(sandboxExtensionHandle));
4381 for (size_t i = 0; i < sandboxExtensionsHandleArray.size(); i++) {
4382 if (auto extension = SandboxExtension::create(WTFMove(sandboxExtensionsHandleArray[i])))
4383 m_pendingDropExtensionsForFileUpload.append(extension);
4384 }
4385
4386 bool handled = m_page->dragController().performDragOperation(dragData);
4387
4388 // If we started loading a local file, the sandbox extension tracker would have adopted this
4389 // pending drop sandbox extension. If not, we'll play it safe and clear it.
4390 m_pendingDropSandboxExtension = nullptr;
4391
4392 m_pendingDropExtensionsForFileUpload.clear();
4393 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformDragOperation(handled));
4394 return;
4395 }
4396 }
4397 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4398}
4399#endif
4400
4401void WebPage::dragEnded(WebCore::IntPoint clientPosition, WebCore::IntPoint globalPosition, OptionSet<WebCore::DragOperation> dragOperationMask)
4402{
4403 IntPoint adjustedClientPosition(clientPosition.x() + m_page->dragController().dragOffset().x(), clientPosition.y() + m_page->dragController().dragOffset().y());
4404 IntPoint adjustedGlobalPosition(globalPosition.x() + m_page->dragController().dragOffset().x(), globalPosition.y() + m_page->dragController().dragOffset().y());
4405
4406 m_page->dragController().dragEnded();
4407 FrameView* view = m_page->mainFrame().view();
4408 if (!view)
4409 return;
4410 // FIXME: These are fake modifier keys here, but they should be real ones instead.
4411 PlatformMouseEvent event(adjustedClientPosition, adjustedGlobalPosition, LeftButton, PlatformEvent::MouseMoved, 0, false, false, false, false, WallTime::now(), 0, WebCore::NoTap);
4412 m_page->mainFrame().eventHandler().dragSourceEndedAt(event, dragOperationMask);
4413
4414 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidEndDragging());
4415
4416 m_isStartingDrag = false;
4417}
4418
4419void WebPage::willPerformLoadDragDestinationAction()
4420{
4421 m_sandboxExtensionTracker.willPerformLoadDragDestinationAction(WTFMove(m_pendingDropSandboxExtension));
4422}
4423
4424void WebPage::mayPerformUploadDragDestinationAction()
4425{
4426 for (size_t i = 0; i < m_pendingDropExtensionsForFileUpload.size(); i++)
4427 m_pendingDropExtensionsForFileUpload[i]->consumePermanently();
4428 m_pendingDropExtensionsForFileUpload.clear();
4429}

4630#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
4631void WebPage::didChooseFilesForOpenPanelWithDisplayStringAndIcon(const Vector<String>& files, const String& displayString, const IPC::DataReference& iconData, SandboxExtension::Handle&& frontboardServicesSandboxExtensionHandle, SandboxExtension::Handle&& iconServicesSandboxExtensionHandle)
4632{
4633 if (!m_activeOpenPanelResultListener)
4634 return;
4635
4636#if HAVE(FRONTBOARD_SYSTEM_APP_SERVICES)
4637 auto frontboardServicesSandboxExtension = SandboxExtension::create(WTFMove(frontboardServicesSandboxExtensionHandle));
4638 if (frontboardServicesSandboxExtension) {
4639 bool consumed = frontboardServicesSandboxExtension->consume();
4640 ASSERT_UNUSED(consumed, consumed);
4641 }
4642 RELEASE_ASSERT(!sandbox_check(getpid(), "mach-lookup", static_cast<enum sandbox_filter_type>(SANDBOX_FILTER_GLOBAL_NAME | SANDBOX_CHECK_NO_REPORT), "com.apple.frontboard.systemappservices"));
4643#endif
4644
4645 auto iconServicesSandboxExtension = SandboxExtension::create(WTFMove(iconServicesSandboxExtensionHandle));
4646 if (iconServicesSandboxExtension) {
4647 bool consumed = iconServicesSandboxExtension->consume();
4648 ASSERT_UNUSED(consumed, consumed);
4649 }
4650 RELEASE_ASSERT(!sandbox_check(getpid(), "mach-lookup", static_cast<enum sandbox_filter_type>(SANDBOX_FILTER_GLOBAL_NAME | SANDBOX_CHECK_NO_REPORT), "com.apple.iconservices"));
4651
4652 RefPtr<Icon> icon;
4653 if (!iconData.isEmpty()) {
4654 RetainPtr<CFDataRef> dataRef = adoptCF(CFDataCreate(nullptr, iconData.data(), iconData.size()));
4655 RetainPtr<CGDataProviderRef> imageProviderRef = adoptCF(CGDataProviderCreateWithCFData(dataRef.get()));
4656 RetainPtr<CGImageRef> imageRef = adoptCF(CGImageCreateWithJPEGDataProvider(imageProviderRef.get(), nullptr, true, kCGRenderingIntentDefault));
4657 icon = Icon::createIconForImage(WTFMove(imageRef));
4658 }
4659
4660 m_activeOpenPanelResultListener->didChooseFilesWithDisplayStringAndIcon(files, displayString, icon.get());
4661 m_activeOpenPanelResultListener = nullptr;
4662
4663#if HAVE(FRONTBOARD_SYSTEM_APP_SERVICES)
4664 if (frontboardServicesSandboxExtension) {
4665 bool revoked = frontboardServicesSandboxExtension->revoke();
4666 ASSERT_UNUSED(revoked, revoked);
4667 }
4668#endif
4669
4670 if (iconServicesSandboxExtension) {
4671 bool revoked = iconServicesSandboxExtension->revoke();
4672 ASSERT_UNUSED(revoked, revoked);
4673 }
4674
4675}
4676#endif

4863
4864void WebPage::updateMainFrameScrollOffsetPinning()
4865{
4866 Frame& frame = m_page->mainFrame();
4867 ScrollPosition scrollPosition = frame.view()->scrollPosition();
4868 ScrollPosition maximumScrollPosition = frame.view()->maximumScrollPosition();
4869 ScrollPosition minimumScrollPosition = frame.view()->minimumScrollPosition();
4870
4871 bool isPinnedToLeftSide = (scrollPosition.x() <= minimumScrollPosition.x());
4872 bool isPinnedToRightSide = (scrollPosition.x() >= maximumScrollPosition.x());
4873 bool isPinnedToTopSide = (scrollPosition.y() <= minimumScrollPosition.y());
4874 bool isPinnedToBottomSide = (scrollPosition.y() >= maximumScrollPosition.y());
4875
4876 if (isPinnedToLeftSide != m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToLeftSide || isPinnedToRightSide != m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToRightSide || isPinnedToTopSide != m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToTopSide || isPinnedToBottomSide != m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToBottomSide) {
4877 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidChangeScrollOffsetPinningForMainFrame(isPinnedToLeftSide, isPinnedToRightSide, isPinnedToTopSide, isPinnedToBottomSide));
4878
4879 m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToLeftSide = isPinnedToLeftSide;
4880 m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToRightSide = isPinnedToRightSide;
4881 m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToTopSide = isPinnedToTopSide;
4882 m_cachedMainFrameIsPinnedToBottomSide = isPinnedToBottomSide;
4883 }
4884}
4885
4886void WebPage::mainFrameDidLayout()
4887{
4888 unsigned pageCount = m_page->pageCount();
4889 if (pageCount != m_cachedPageCount) {
4890 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidChangePageCount(pageCount));
4891 m_cachedPageCount = pageCount;
4892 }
4893
4894#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || PLATFORM(GTK)
4895 if (m_viewGestureGeometryCollector)
4896 m_viewGestureGeometryCollector->mainFrameDidLayout();
4897#endif
4898#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
4899 if (FrameView* frameView = mainFrameView()) {
4900 IntSize newContentSize = frameView->contentsSize();
4901 LOG_WITH_STREAM(VisibleRects, stream << "WebPage " << m_identifier.toUInt64() << " mainFrameDidLayout setting content size to " << newContentSize);
4902 if (m_viewportConfiguration.setContentsSize(newContentSize))
4903 viewportConfigurationChanged();
4904 }
4905 findController().redraw();
4906#endif
4907}

4933void WebPage::windowAndViewFramesChanged(const FloatRect& windowFrameInScreenCoordinates, const FloatRect& windowFrameInUnflippedScreenCoordinates, const FloatRect& viewFrameInWindowCoordinates, const FloatPoint& accessibilityViewCoordinates)
4934{

4971
4972void WebPage::didReceiveMessage(IPC::Connection& connection, IPC::Decoder& decoder)
4973{
4974 if (decoder.messageReceiverName() == Messages::WebInspector::messageReceiverName()) {
4975 if (WebInspector* inspector = this->inspector())
4976 inspector->didReceiveMessage(connection, decoder);
4977 return;
4978 }
4979
4980 if (decoder.messageReceiverName() == Messages::WebInspectorUI::messageReceiverName()) {
4981 if (WebInspectorUI* inspectorUI = this->inspectorUI())
4982 inspectorUI->didReceiveMessage(connection, decoder);
4983 return;
4984 }
4985
4986 if (decoder.messageReceiverName() == Messages::RemoteWebInspectorUI::messageReceiverName()) {
4987 if (RemoteWebInspectorUI* remoteInspectorUI = this->remoteInspectorUI())
4988 remoteInspectorUI->didReceiveMessage(connection, decoder);
4989 return;
4990 }
4991
4992#if ENABLE(FULLSCREEN_API)
4993 if (decoder.messageReceiverName() == Messages::WebFullScreenManager::messageReceiverName()) {
4994 fullScreenManager()->didReceiveMessage(connection, decoder);
4995 return;
4996 }
4997#endif
4998
4999 didReceiveWebPageMessage(connection, decoder);
5000}
5001
5002bool WebPage::didReceiveSyncMessage(IPC::Connection& connection, IPC::Decoder& decoder, UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>& replyEncoder)
5003{
5004 return didReceiveSyncWebPageMessage(connection, decoder, replyEncoder);
5005}

5010 return m_page->scrollingCoordinator();

5013
5014WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::~SandboxExtensionTracker()
5015{
5016 invalidate();
5017}
5018
5019void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::invalidate()
5020{
5021 m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension = nullptr;
5022
5023 if (m_provisionalSandboxExtension) {
5024 m_provisionalSandboxExtension->revoke();
5025 m_provisionalSandboxExtension = nullptr;
5026 }
5027
5028 if (m_committedSandboxExtension) {
5029 m_committedSandboxExtension->revoke();
5030 m_committedSandboxExtension = nullptr;
5031 }
5032}
5033
5034void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::willPerformLoadDragDestinationAction(RefPtr<SandboxExtension>&& pendingDropSandboxExtension)
5035{
5036 setPendingProvisionalSandboxExtension(WTFMove(pendingDropSandboxExtension));
5037}
5038
5039void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::beginLoad(WebFrame* frame, SandboxExtension::Handle&& handle)
5040{
5041 ASSERT_UNUSED(frame, frame->isMainFrame());
5042
5043 setPendingProvisionalSandboxExtension(SandboxExtension::create(WTFMove(handle)));
5044}
5045
5046void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::beginReload(WebFrame* frame, SandboxExtension::Handle&& handle)
5047{
5048 ASSERT_UNUSED(frame, frame->isMainFrame());
5049
5050 // Maintain existing provisional SandboxExtension in case of a reload, if the new handle is null. This is needed
5051 // because the UIProcess sends us a null handle if it already sent us a handle for this path in the past.
5052 if (auto sandboxExtension = SandboxExtension::create(WTFMove(handle)))
5053 setPendingProvisionalSandboxExtension(WTFMove(sandboxExtension));
5054}
5055
5056void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::setPendingProvisionalSandboxExtension(RefPtr<SandboxExtension>&& pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension)
5057{
5058 m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension = WTFMove(pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension);
5059}
5060
5061bool WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::shouldReuseCommittedSandboxExtension(WebFrame* frame)
5062{
5063 ASSERT(frame->isMainFrame());
5064
5065 FrameLoader& frameLoader = frame->coreFrame()->loader();
5066 FrameLoadType frameLoadType = frameLoader.loadType();
5067
5068 // If the page is being reloaded, it should reuse whatever extension is committed.
5069 if (isReload(frameLoadType))
5070 return true;
5071
5072 if (m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension)
5073 return false;
5074
5075 DocumentLoader* documentLoader = frameLoader.documentLoader();
5076 DocumentLoader* provisionalDocumentLoader = frameLoader.provisionalDocumentLoader();
5077 if (!documentLoader || !provisionalDocumentLoader)
5078 return false;
5079
5080 if (documentLoader->url().isLocalFile() && provisionalDocumentLoader->url().isLocalFile())
5081 return true;
5082
5083 return false;
5084}
5085
5086void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::didStartProvisionalLoad(WebFrame* frame)
5087{
5088 if (!frame->isMainFrame())
5089 return;
5090
5091 // We should only reuse the commited sandbox extension if it is not null. It can be
5092 // null if the last load was for an error page.
5093 if (m_committedSandboxExtension && shouldReuseCommittedSandboxExtension(frame))
5094 m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension = m_committedSandboxExtension;
5095
5096 ASSERT(!m_provisionalSandboxExtension);
5097
5098 m_provisionalSandboxExtension = WTFMove(m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension);
5099 if (!m_provisionalSandboxExtension)
5100 return;
5101
5102 m_provisionalSandboxExtension->consume();
5103}
5104
5105void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::didCommitProvisionalLoad(WebFrame* frame)
5106{
5107 if (!frame->isMainFrame())
5108 return;
5109
5110 if (m_committedSandboxExtension)
5111 m_committedSandboxExtension->revoke();
5112
5113 m_committedSandboxExtension = WTFMove(m_provisionalSandboxExtension);
5114
5115 // We can also have a non-null m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension if a new load is being started.
5116 // This extension is not cleared, because it does not pertain to the failed load, and will be needed.
5117}
5118
5119void WebPage::SandboxExtensionTracker::didFailProvisionalLoad(WebFrame* frame)
5120{
5121 if (!frame->isMainFrame())
5122 return;
5123
5124 if (!m_provisionalSandboxExtension)
5125 return;
5126
5127 m_provisionalSandboxExtension->revoke();
5128 m_provisionalSandboxExtension = nullptr;
5129
5130 // We can also have a non-null m_pendingProvisionalSandboxExtension if a new load is being started
5131 // (notably, if the current one fails because the new one cancels it). This extension is not cleared,
5132 // because it does not pertain to the failed load, and will be needed.
5133}
5134
5135bool WebPage::hasLocalDataForURL(const URL& url)
5136{
5137 if (url.isLocalFile())
5138 return true;
5139
5140 DocumentLoader* documentLoader = m_page->mainFrame().loader().documentLoader();
5141 if (documentLoader && documentLoader->subresource(url))
5142 return true;
5143
5144 return false;
5145}

5209
5210void WebPage::beginPrinting(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo)
5211{
5212 PrintContextAccessScope scope { *this };
5213
5214 WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
5215 if (!frame)
5216 return;
5217
5218 Frame* coreFrame = frame->coreFrame();
5219 if (!coreFrame)
5220 return;
5221
5222#if PLATFORM(MAC)
5223 if (pdfDocumentForPrintingFrame(coreFrame))
5224 return;
5225#endif
5226
5227 if (!m_printContext) {
5228 m_printContext = makeUnique<PrintContext>(coreFrame);
5229 m_page->dispatchBeforePrintEvent();
5230 }
5231
5232 freezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::Printing);
5233
5234 auto computedPageSize = m_printContext->computedPageSize(FloatSize(printInfo.availablePaperWidth, printInfo.availablePaperHeight), printInfo.margin);
5235
5236 m_printContext->begin(computedPageSize.width(), computedPageSize.height());
5237
5238 // PrintContext::begin() performed a synchronous layout which might have executed a
5239 // script that closed the WebPage, clearing m_printContext.
5240 // See <rdar://problem/49731211> for cases of this happening.
5241 if (!m_printContext) {
5242 unfreezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::Printing);
5243 return;
5244 }
5245
5246 float fullPageHeight;
5247 m_printContext->computePageRects(FloatRect(0, 0, computedPageSize.width(), computedPageSize.height()), 0, 0, printInfo.pageSetupScaleFactor, fullPageHeight, true);
5248
5249#if PLATFORM(GTK)
5250 if (!m_printOperation)
5251 m_printOperation = WebPrintOperationGtk::create(this, printInfo);
5252#endif
5253}
5254
5255void WebPage::endPrinting()
5256{
5257 if (m_inActivePrintContextAccessScope) {
5258 m_shouldEndPrintingImmediately = true;
5259 return;
5260 }
5261 endPrintingImmediately();
5262}
5263
5264void WebPage::endPrintingImmediately()
5265{
5266 RELEASE_ASSERT(!m_inActivePrintContextAccessScope);
5267 m_shouldEndPrintingImmediately = false;
5268
5269 unfreezeLayerTree(LayerTreeFreezeReason::Printing);
5270
5271 if (m_printContext) {
5272 m_printContext = nullptr;
5273 m_page->dispatchAfterPrintEvent();
5274 }
5275}
5276
5277void WebPage::computePagesForPrinting(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo, CompletionHandler<void(const Vector<WebCore::IntRect>&, double, const WebCore::FloatBoxExtent&)>&& completionHandler)
5278{
5279 PrintContextAccessScope scope { *this };
5280 Vector<IntRect> resultPageRects;
5281 double resultTotalScaleFactorForPrinting = 1;
5282 auto computedPageMargin = printInfo.margin;
5283 computePagesForPrintingImpl(frameID, printInfo, resultPageRects, resultTotalScaleFactorForPrinting, computedPageMargin);
5284 completionHandler(resultPageRects, resultTotalScaleFactorForPrinting, computedPageMargin);
5285}
5286
5287void WebPage::computePagesForPrintingImpl(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo, Vector<WebCore::IntRect>& resultPageRects, double& resultTotalScaleFactorForPrinting, FloatBoxExtent& computedPageMargin)
5288{
5289 ASSERT(resultPageRects.isEmpty());
5290
5291 beginPrinting(frameID, printInfo);
5292
5293 if (m_printContext) {
5294 PrintContextAccessScope scope { *this };
5295 resultPageRects = m_printContext->pageRects();
5296 computedPageMargin = m_printContext->computedPageMargin(printInfo.margin);
5297 auto computedPageSize = m_printContext->computedPageSize(FloatSize(printInfo.availablePaperWidth, printInfo.availablePaperHeight), printInfo.margin);
5298 resultTotalScaleFactorForPrinting = m_printContext->computeAutomaticScaleFactor(computedPageSize) * printInfo.pageSetupScaleFactor;
5299 }
5300#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
5301 else
5302 computePagesForPrintingPDFDocument(frameID, printInfo, resultPageRects);
5303#endif // PLATFORM(COCOA)
5304
5305 // If we're asked to print, we should actually print at least a blank page.
5306 if (resultPageRects.isEmpty())
5307 resultPageRects.append(IntRect(0, 0, 1, 1));
5308}
5309
5310#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
5311void WebPage::drawToPDF(FrameIdentifier frameID, const std::optional<FloatRect>& rect, CompletionHandler<void(const IPC::DataReference&)>&& completionHandler)
5312{
5313 auto& frameView = *m_page->mainFrame().view();
5314 IntSize snapshotSize;
5315 if (rect)
5316 snapshotSize = IntSize(rect->size());
5317 else
5318 snapshotSize = { frameView.contentsSize() };
5319
5320 IntRect snapshotRect;
5321 if (rect)
5322 snapshotRect = { {(int)rect->x(), (int)rect->y()}, snapshotSize };
5323 else
5324 snapshotRect = { {0, 0}, snapshotSize };
5325
5326 auto originalLayoutViewportOverrideRect = frameView.layoutViewportOverrideRect();
5327 frameView.setLayoutViewportOverrideRect(LayoutRect(snapshotRect));
5328 auto originalPaintBehavior = frameView.paintBehavior();
5329 frameView.setPaintBehavior(originalPaintBehavior | PaintBehavior::AnnotateLinks);
5330
5331 auto pdfData = pdfSnapshotAtSize(snapshotRect, snapshotSize, 0);
5332
5333 frameView.setLayoutViewportOverrideRect(originalLayoutViewportOverrideRect);
5334 frameView.setPaintBehavior(originalPaintBehavior);
5335
5336 completionHandler(IPC::DataReference(CFDataGetBytePtr(pdfData.get()), CFDataGetLength(pdfData.get())));
5337}
5338
5339void WebPage::drawRectToImage(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo, const IntRect& rect, const WebCore::IntSize& imageSize, CompletionHandler<void(const WebKit::ShareableBitmap::Handle&)>&& completionHandler)
5340{
5341 PrintContextAccessScope scope { *this };
5342 WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
5343 Frame* coreFrame = frame ? frame->coreFrame() : 0;
5344
5345 RefPtr<WebImage> image;
5346
5347#if USE(CG)
5348 if (coreFrame) {
5349#if PLATFORM(MAC)
5350 ASSERT(coreFrame->document()->printing() || pdfDocumentForPrintingFrame(coreFrame));
5351#else
5352 ASSERT(coreFrame->document()->printing());
5353#endif
5354
5355 auto bitmap = ShareableBitmap::createShareable(imageSize, { });
5356 if (!bitmap) {
5357 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
5358 return completionHandler({ });
5359 }
5360 auto graphicsContext = bitmap->createGraphicsContext();
5361 if (graphicsContext) {
5362 float printingScale = static_cast<float>(imageSize.width()) / rect.width();
5363 graphicsContext->scale(printingScale);
5364
5365#if PLATFORM(MAC)
5366 if (RetainPtr<PDFDocument> pdfDocument = pdfDocumentForPrintingFrame(coreFrame)) {
5367 ASSERT(!m_printContext);
5368 graphicsContext->scale(FloatSize(1, -1));
5369 graphicsContext->translate(0, -rect.height());
5370 drawPDFDocument(graphicsContext->platformContext(), pdfDocument.get(), printInfo, rect);
5371 } else
5372#endif
5373 {
5374 m_printContext->spoolRect(*graphicsContext, rect);
5375 }
5376 }
5377
5378 image = WebImage::create(bitmap.releaseNonNull());
5379 }
5380#endif
5381
5382 ShareableBitmap::Handle handle;
5383
5384 if (image)
5385 image->bitmap().createHandle(handle, SharedMemory::Protection::ReadOnly);
5386
5387 completionHandler(handle);
5388}
5389
5390void WebPage::drawPagesToPDF(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo, uint32_t first, uint32_t count, CompletionHandler<void(const IPC::DataReference&)>&& callback)
5391{
5392 PrintContextAccessScope scope { *this };
5393 RetainPtr<CFMutableDataRef> pdfPageData;
5394 drawPagesToPDFImpl(frameID, printInfo, first, count, pdfPageData);
5395 callback({ CFDataGetBytePtr(pdfPageData.get()), static_cast<size_t>(CFDataGetLength(pdfPageData.get())) });
5396}
5397
5398void WebPage::drawPagesToPDFImpl(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo, uint32_t first, uint32_t count, RetainPtr<CFMutableDataRef>& pdfPageData)
5399{
5400 WebFrame* frame = WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(frameID);
5401 Frame* coreFrame = frame ? frame->coreFrame() : 0;
5402
5403 pdfPageData = adoptCF(CFDataCreateMutable(0, 0));
5404
5405#if USE(CG)
5406 if (coreFrame) {
5407
5408#if PLATFORM(MAC)
5409 ASSERT(coreFrame->document()->printing() || pdfDocumentForPrintingFrame(coreFrame));
5410#else
5411 ASSERT(coreFrame->document()->printing());
5412#endif
5413
5414 // FIXME: Use CGDataConsumerCreate with callbacks to avoid copying the data.
5415 RetainPtr<CGDataConsumerRef> pdfDataConsumer = adoptCF(CGDataConsumerCreateWithCFData(pdfPageData.get()));
5416
5417 CGRect mediaBox = (m_printContext && m_printContext->pageCount()) ? m_printContext->pageRect(0) : CGRectMake(0, 0, printInfo.availablePaperWidth, printInfo.availablePaperHeight);
5418 RetainPtr<CGContextRef> context = adoptCF(CGPDFContextCreate(pdfDataConsumer.get(), &mediaBox, 0));
5419
5420#if PLATFORM(MAC)
5421 if (RetainPtr<PDFDocument> pdfDocument = pdfDocumentForPrintingFrame(coreFrame)) {
5422 ASSERT(!m_printContext);
5423 drawPagesToPDFFromPDFDocument(context.get(), pdfDocument.get(), printInfo, first, count);
5424 } else
5425#endif
5426 {
5427 size_t pageCount = m_printContext->pageCount();
5428 for (uint32_t page = first; page < first + count; ++page) {
5429 if (page >= pageCount)
5430 break;
5431
5432 RetainPtr<CFDictionaryRef> pageInfo = adoptCF(CFDictionaryCreateMutable(0, 0, &kCFTypeDictionaryKeyCallBacks, &kCFTypeDictionaryValueCallBacks));
5433 CGPDFContextBeginPage(context.get(), pageInfo.get());
5434
5435 GraphicsContextCG ctx(context.get());
5436 ctx.scale(FloatSize(1, -1));
5437 ctx.translate(0, -m_printContext->pageRect(page).height());
5438 m_printContext->spoolPage(ctx, page, m_printContext->pageRect(page).width());
5439
5440 CGPDFContextEndPage(context.get());
5441 }
5442 }
5443 CGPDFContextClose(context.get());
5444 }
5445#endif
5446}
5447
5448#elif PLATFORM(GTK)
5449void WebPage::drawPagesForPrinting(FrameIdentifier frameID, const PrintInfo& printInfo, CompletionHandler<void(const WebCore::ResourceError&)>&& completionHandler)

5454 m_printOperation = nullptr;
5455 completionHandler(error);
5456 });
5457 return;
5458 }
5459 completionHandler({ });
5460}

5475void WebPage::addResourceRequest(unsigned long identifier, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& request)
5476{
5477 if (!request.url().protocolIsInHTTPFamily())
5478 return;
5479
5480 if (m_mainFrameProgressCompleted && !UserGestureIndicator::processingUserGesture())
5481 return;
5482
5483 ASSERT(!m_trackedNetworkResourceRequestIdentifiers.contains(identifier));
5484 bool wasEmpty = m_trackedNetworkResourceRequestIdentifiers.isEmpty();
5485 m_trackedNetworkResourceRequestIdentifiers.add(identifier);
5486 if (wasEmpty)
5487 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetNetworkRequestsInProgress(true));
5488}
5489
5490void WebPage::removeResourceRequest(unsigned long identifier)
5491{
5492 if (!m_trackedNetworkResourceRequestIdentifiers.remove(identifier))
5493 return;
5494
5495 if (m_trackedNetworkResourceRequestIdentifiers.isEmpty())
5496 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetNetworkRequestsInProgress(false));
5497}

5528void WebPage::runModal()

5531 return;
5532 if (m_isRunningModal)
5533 return;

5536 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::RunModal());
5537#if ASSERT_ENABLED

5539#endif

5541 ASSERT(!m_isRunningModal);
5542}

5544bool WebPage::canHandleRequest(const WebCore::ResourceRequest& request)
5545{
5546 if (LegacySchemeRegistry::shouldLoadURLSchemeAsEmptyDocument(request.url().protocol().toStringWithoutCopying()))
5547 return true;
5548
5549 if (request.url().protocolIsBlob())
5550 return true;
5551
5552 return platformCanHandleRequest(request);
5553}

5618
5619static bool hasEnabledHorizontalScrollbar(ScrollableArea* scrollableArea)
5620{
5621 if (Scrollbar* scrollbar = scrollableArea->horizontalScrollbar())
5622 return scrollbar->enabled();
5623
5624 return false;
5625}
5626
5627static bool pageContainsAnyHorizontalScrollbars(Frame* mainFrame)
5628{
5629 if (FrameView* frameView = mainFrame->view()) {
5630 if (hasEnabledHorizontalScrollbar(frameView))
5631 return true;
5632 }
5633
5634 for (Frame* frame = mainFrame; frame; frame = frame->tree().traverseNext()) {
5635 FrameView* frameView = frame->view();
5636 if (!frameView)
5637 continue;
5638
5639 const HashSet<ScrollableArea*>* scrollableAreas = frameView->scrollableAreas();
5640 if (!scrollableAreas)
5641 continue;
5642
5643 for (HashSet<ScrollableArea*>::const_iterator it = scrollableAreas->begin(), end = scrollableAreas->end(); it != end; ++it) {
5644 ScrollableArea* scrollableArea = *it;
5645 if (!scrollableArea->scrollbarsCanBeActive())
5646 continue;
5647
5648 if (hasEnabledHorizontalScrollbar(scrollableArea))
5649 return true;
5650 }
5651 }
5652
5653 return false;
5654}
5655
5656void WebPage::recomputeShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEventsState()
5657{
5658 bool canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents = !m_hasWheelEventHandlers;
5659
5660 if (canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents) {
5661 // Check if we have any horizontal scroll bars on the page.
5662 if (pageContainsAnyHorizontalScrollbars(mainFrame()))
5663 canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents = false;
5664 }
5665
5666 if (m_canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents == canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents)
5667 return;
5668
5669 m_canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents = canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents;
5670 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetCanShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents(m_canShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEvents));
5671}
5672
5673Frame* WebPage::mainFrame() const
5674{
5675 return m_page ? &m_page->mainFrame() : nullptr;
5676}
5677
5678FrameView* WebPage::mainFrameView() const
5679{
5680 if (Frame* frame = mainFrame())
5681 return frame->view();
5682
5683 return nullptr;
5684}
5685
5686bool WebPage::canPluginHandleResponse(const ResourceResponse& response)
5687{
5688#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
5689 uint32_t pluginLoadPolicy;
5690 bool allowOnlyApplicationPlugins = !m_mainFrame->coreFrame()->arePluginsEnabled();
5691
5692 uint64_t pluginProcessToken;
5693 String newMIMEType;
5694 String unavailabilityDescription;
5695 bool isUnsupported = false;
5696 if (!sendSync(Messages::WebPageProxy::FindPlugin(response.mimeType(), response.url().string(), response.url().string(), response.url().string(), allowOnlyApplicationPlugins), Messages::WebPageProxy::FindPlugin::Reply(pluginProcessToken, newMIMEType, pluginLoadPolicy, unavailabilityDescription, isUnsupported)))
5697 return false;
5698
5699 ASSERT(!isUnsupported);
5700 bool isBlockedPlugin = (pluginLoadPolicy == PluginModuleBlockedForSecurity) || (pluginLoadPolicy == PluginModuleBlockedForCompatibility);
5701 return !isUnsupported && !isBlockedPlugin && pluginProcessToken;
5702#else
5703 UNUSED_PARAM(response);
5704 return false;
5705#endif
5706}
5707
5708bool WebPage::shouldUseCustomContentProviderForResponse(const ResourceResponse& response)
5709{
5710 auto& mimeType = response.mimeType();
5711 if (mimeType.isNull())
5712 return false;
5713
5714 // If a plug-in exists that claims to support this response, it should take precedence over the custom content provider.
5715 // canPluginHandleResponse() is called last because it performs synchronous IPC.
5716 return m_mimeTypesWithCustomContentProviders.contains(mimeType) && !canPluginHandleResponse(response);
5717}

5719#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
5720
5721void WebPage::setTextAsync(const String& text)
5722{
5723 auto frame = makeRef(m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame());
5724 if (frame->selection().selection().isContentEditable()) {
5725 UserTypingGestureIndicator indicator(frame.get());
5726 frame->selection().selectAll();
5727 if (text.isEmpty())
5728 frame->editor().deleteSelectionWithSmartDelete(false);
5729 else
5730 frame->editor().insertText(text, nullptr, TextEventInputKeyboard);
5731 return;
5732 }
5733
5734 if (is<HTMLInputElement>(m_focusedElement.get())) {
5735 downcast<HTMLInputElement>(*m_focusedElement).setValueForUser(text);
5736 return;
5737 }
5738
5739 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
5740}
5741
5742void WebPage::insertTextAsync(const String& text, const EditingRange& replacementEditingRange, InsertTextOptions&& options)
5743{
5744 platformWillPerformEditingCommand();
5745
5746 auto& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
5747
5748 Ref<Frame> protector(frame);
5749
5750 UserGestureIndicator gestureIndicator { options.processingUserGesture ? ProcessingUserGesture : NotProcessingUserGesture, frame.document() };
5751
5752 bool replacesText = false;
5753 if (replacementEditingRange.location != notFound) {
5754 if (auto replacementRange = EditingRange::toRange(frame, replacementEditingRange, options.editingRangeIsRelativeTo)) {
5755 SetForScope<bool> isSelectingTextWhileInsertingAsynchronously(m_isSelectingTextWhileInsertingAsynchronously, options.suppressSelectionUpdate);
5756 frame.selection().setSelection(VisibleSelection(*replacementRange));
5757 replacesText = replacementEditingRange.length;
5758 }
5759 }
5760
5761 if (options.registerUndoGroup)
5762 send(Messages::WebPageProxy::RegisterInsertionUndoGrouping());
5763
5764 RefPtr<Element> focusedElement = frame.document() ? frame.document()->focusedElement() : nullptr;
5765 if (focusedElement && options.shouldSimulateKeyboardInput)
5766 focusedElement->dispatchEvent(Event::create(eventNames().keydownEvent, Event::CanBubble::Yes, Event::IsCancelable::Yes));
5767
5768 if (!frame.editor().hasComposition()) {
5769 // An insertText: might be handled by other responders in the chain if we don't handle it.
5770 // One example is space bar that results in scrolling down the page.
5771 frame.editor().insertText(text, nullptr, replacesText ? TextEventInputAutocompletion : TextEventInputKeyboard);
5772 } else
5773 frame.editor().confirmComposition(text);
5774
5775 if (focusedElement && options.shouldSimulateKeyboardInput) {
5776 focusedElement->dispatchEvent(Event::create(eventNames().keyupEvent, Event::CanBubble::Yes, Event::IsCancelable::Yes));
5777 focusedElement->dispatchEvent(Event::create(eventNames().changeEvent, Event::CanBubble::Yes, Event::IsCancelable::Yes));
5778 }
5779}

5781void WebPage::hasMarkedText(CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
5782{
5783 completionHandler(m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame().editor().hasComposition());
5784}

5797
5798void WebPage::characterIndexForPointAsync(const WebCore::IntPoint& point, CompletionHandler<void(uint64_t)>&& completionHandler)
5799{
5800 constexpr OptionSet<HitTestRequest::Type> hitType { HitTestRequest::Type::ReadOnly, HitTestRequest::Type::Active, HitTestRequest::Type::DisallowUserAgentShadowContent, HitTestRequest::Type::AllowChildFrameContent };
5801 auto result = m_page->mainFrame().eventHandler().hitTestResultAtPoint(point, hitType);
5802 auto& frame = result.innerNonSharedNode() ? *result.innerNodeFrame() : m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
5803 auto range = frame.rangeForPoint(result.roundedPointInInnerNodeFrame());
5804 auto editingRange = EditingRange::fromRange(frame, range);
5805 completionHandler(editingRange.location);
5806}
5807
5808void WebPage::firstRectForCharacterRangeAsync(const EditingRange& editingRange, CompletionHandler<void(const WebCore::IntRect&, const EditingRange&)>&& completionHandler)
5809{
5810 auto& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
5811 auto range = EditingRange::toRange(frame, editingRange);
5812 if (!range)
5813 return completionHandler({ }, { });
5814
5815 // FIXME: Pass an EditingRange that matches the range of the first rect, rather than the entire passed-in range?
5816 auto rect = frame.view()->contentsToWindow(frame.editor().firstRectForRange(*range));
5817 completionHandler(rect, editingRange);
5818}

5820void WebPage::setCompositionAsync(const String& text, const Vector<CompositionUnderline>& underlines, const Vector<CompositionHighlight>& highlights, const EditingRange& selection, const EditingRange& replacementEditingRange)
5821{
5822 platformWillPerformEditingCommand();
5823
5824 auto& frame = m_page->focusController().focusedOrMainFrame();
5825 if (frame.selection().selection().isContentEditable()) {
5826 if (replacementEditingRange.location != notFound) {
5827 if (auto replacementRange = EditingRange::toRange(frame, replacementEditingRange))
5828 frame.selection().setSelection(VisibleSelection(*replacementRange));
5829 }
5830 frame.editor().setComposition(text, underlines, highlights, selection.location, selection.location + selection.length);
5831 }
5832}

5835{
5836 platformWillPerformEditingCommand();

5839 frame.editor().confirmComposition();
5840}
